T03TD3790.3E:96b-27: kun chub par byed pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:96b-28: tshul bzhin du yid la byed pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:96b-29: gzhan la yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo 'di rnam grangs du mar rgya cher pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-6: yang dag par ston pa'i rigs kyi bu dang rigs kyi bu mo de ni myur du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-7: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang nye bar gyur pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:97a-9: kun dga' bo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa las byung ba ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub ste /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-10: kun dga' bo 'das pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig byung ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gi bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid las byung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:97a-11: kun dga' bo ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig byung ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gi bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid las 'byung bar 'gyur ro ;
T03TD3790.3E:97a-12: / kun dga' bo da ltar byung ba'i dus na shar phyogs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-21: steng gi 'jig rten gyi khams grangs med tshad med dpag tu med pa dag na de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig bzhugs shing 'tsho skyong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-22: chos ston pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gi bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid las byung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:97a-23: kun dga' bo de bas na bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'dod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:97a-24: pha rol tu phyin pa drug la slob par 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo 'di la bslab par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-2: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi ma ste skyed par byed pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-3: kun dga' bo byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang pha rol tu phyin pa drug la slob pa de dag thams cad ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'byung bar 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:97b-4: kun dga' bo de bas na khyod la pha rol tu phyin pa drug po 'di dag yang dang yang yongs su gtad do //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-7: kun dga' bo 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos kyi mdzod mi zad pa'i mdzod de /
T03TD3790.3E:97b-8: 'di lta ste shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdzod do //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-9: kun dga' bo phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams tshad med grangs med dpag tu med pa dag na /
T03TD3790.3E:97b-10: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig bzhugs shing 'tsho skyong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:97b-11: chos ston pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag kyang pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi mdzod 'di las chos ston to //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-12: kun dga' bo 'das pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig byung ba de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid la bslabs nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te chos ston to //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-13: kun dga' bo ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig 'byung ba de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid la bslab ste /
T03TD3790.3E:97b-14: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur te chos kyang ston par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:97b-17: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi nyan thos gang ji snyed cig yod pa de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid la bslabs te yongs su mya ngan las 'das par gyur to //
T03TD3790.3E:98a-1: 'da' bar 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni byang chub chen po'i rgyu shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su gtad pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:98a-2: kun dga' bo gal te khyod kyis gang zag nyan thos kyi theg pa ba rnams la nyan thos kyi sa las brtsams te chos ston pa'i chos bstan pa des stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can gang ji snyed pa de dag thams cad dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byed par gyur kyang da dung nyan thos kyis nga'i nyan thos kyi bya ba byas par mi 'gyur gyi /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-3: kun dga' bo gal te khyod kyis byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang ldan pa'i tshig 'ga' zhig brjod pa de bstan kyang nyan thos kyis nga dgyes par byas pa ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-4: nyan thos kyis nyan thos kyi bya ba byas par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:98a-5: kun dga' bo de ji snyam du sems /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-6: chos bstan pa snga ma des stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can gang ji snyed pa de dag thams cad snga phyi med par mi'i lus thob par gyur la /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-7: mi'i lus thob nas kyang dgra bcom pa nyid mngon du byas par gyur na /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-8: dgra bcom pa de dag gis sbyin pa las byung ba'i bsod nams bya ba'i dngos po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-9: tshul khrims las byung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-10: bsgoms pa las byung ba'i bsod nams bya ba'i dngos po de dag mang ngam /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-13: bde bar gshegs pa mang ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:98a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-15: kun dga' bo de bas gang zag nyan thos kyi theg pa pa gang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la chung ngu na nyi ma gcig cig shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang ldan pa'i chos ston na /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-16: de'i bsod nams ches mang du 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:98a-17: kun dga' bo nyin gcig lta zhog gi gal te nyi ma phyed dam /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-18: kun dga' bo nyi ma phyed lta zhog gi / gal te snga dro gcig gam /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-19: kun dga' bo snga dro gcig lta zhog gi / gal te chu tshod gcig tsam mam /
T03TD3790.3E:98a-20: kun dga' bo chu tshod gcig tsam lta zhog gi / gal te skad cig gam /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-0: tha na mig 'dzums @98b pa tsam gyi tshod du yang gang zag nyan thos kyi theg pa bas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang ldan pa'i chos bstan na /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-1: kun dga' bo de'i bsod nams ches mang du 'phel bar 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-3: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa pa'i rigs kyi bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-4: rigs kyi bu mo de dag thams cad kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba yang des zil gyis non par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:98b-5: kun dga' bo gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang zag byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa pa rnams la chung du na nyi ma gcig gam /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-11: thang 'ga' zhig shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang ldan pa'i chos ston na /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-12: kun dga' bo byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des nyan thos dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-13: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa pa'i rigs kyi bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-14: rigs kyi bu mo de dag thams cad kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba zil gyis non par 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-16: 'di ltar de ni bdag kyang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'dod la /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-17: gzhan yang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par dga' bar byed pa yin /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-19: yang dag par 'dzin du 'jug / yang dag par 'god par byed /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-20: yang dag par rab tu gnas par byed pa'i phyir te /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-21: kun dga' bo de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po pha rol tu phyin pa drug la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-22: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-23: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-24: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-27: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-28: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-32: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-33: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:98b-34: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-2: mngon par shes pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-4: gzungs kyi sgo rnams la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-5: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-7: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-8: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-9: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar la spyod pa de dag dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par 'phel ba ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las yongs su nyams pa'i gnas med skabs med de de ni gnas ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:99a-10: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di bshad pa'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-19: lto 'phye chen po de ltar 'khod pa rnams kyi mdun du rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad pa gang mngon par 'du mdzad pas /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-20: thams cad kyis de bzhin gshegs pa sgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa 'khor rgya mtsho lta bu 'khrugs pa med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-25: sems shin tu rnam par grol ba /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-26: shes rab shin tu rnam par grol ba /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-32: rang gi don rjes su thob pa /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-35: yang dag par kun shes pas sems shin tu rnam par grol ba /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-36: sems can thams cad la dbang dam pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa thob pa sha stag gi dge slong gi dge 'dun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-37: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sha stag gis kun nas bskor zhing mdun du bdar ba mthong bar 'gyur ba de lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad pa mngon par 'du mdzad do //
T03TD3790.3E:99a-38: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad pa de phyir brtul bar gyur to /
T03TD3790.3E:99a-39: rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad pa de phyir brtul bar gyur nas /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-0: 'khor bzhi po de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom @99b pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa de yang ma mthong /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-2: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa pa de dag kyang ma mthong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing de yang ma mthong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-4: sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun yang mig lam du mi snang bar gyur to //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-6: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad pa phyir brtul bar mdzad pas de'i phyir de dag gis ma mthong bar gyur to //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-7: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-8: kun dga' bo khyod kyis de bzhin gshegs pa mi 'khrugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-9: de bzhin gshegs pa sgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-11: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun mthong ngam /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-13: bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas kyi zhing de yang ma mthong /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-14: de bzhin gshegs pa de yang ma mthong /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-15: dge slong gi dge 'dun de yang ma mthong ;
T03TD3790.3E:99b-16: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun de yang ma mthong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-17: mig lam du yang mi gda'o //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-19: kun dga' bo de bzhin du chos thams cad kyang mig lam du snang ba ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-20: chos la chos snang par mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-22: chos kyis chos mi shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-23: kun dga' bo ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-25: gang zag byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa pa de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-26: sangs rgyas kyi zhing de mig lam du snang bar ma gyur pa de bzhin du chos thams cad kyang mig lam du snang ba ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-27: chos la chos snang bar mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:99b-29: chos kyis chos mi shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:99b-30: kun dga' bo chos thams cad ni shes pa med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-2: bya ba la mthu med pa sha stag ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-4: kun dga' bo chos thams cad ni nam mkha' ltar g-yo ba med pa 'dzin pa med pas byed pa med cing 'dzin pa mid pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-5: kun dga' bo chos thams cad ni sgyu ma'i skyes bu lta bu ste bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o ;
T03TD3790.3E:100a-6: / kun dga' bo chos thams cad ni sems dang bral zhing rnam par bsgrub pa la so sor gnas pa'i mtshan nyid de snying po med pa'i phyir tshor ba med pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-7: de ltar spyod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-8: chos gang la yang mngon par chags pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-9: kun dga' bo de ltar slob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la slob pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-10: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po pha rol tu phyin pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par bya bar 'dod pas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la slob par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-11: de ltar slob pa ni rab ces bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-17: bla na med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-18: gong na med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-19: mnyam pa med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-20: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-21: 'jig rten thams cad la phan pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-22: 'jig rten thams cad la bde ba /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-23: mgon med pa rnams la mgon du gyur pa /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-25: sangs rgyas kyis bsngags pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100a-26: de la gnas shing de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di phyag g-yas pas gyen du bteg cing phyir gzhog kyang sems can de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di bteg go zhes bya ba dang gzhog go zhes bya bar mi shes pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100a-28: kun dga' bo sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid la bslabs pas 'das pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-0: da ltar byung ba'i chos rnams la thogs pa @100b mi mnga' ba'i ye shes kyi gzigs pa grub pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-1: kun dga' bo bslab pa gang ji snyed cig yod pa'i bslab pa thams cad kyi nang na shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la bslab pa ni rab ces bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-7: bla na med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-8: gong na med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-9: mnyam pa med pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-10: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-11: kun dga' bo gang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshad gzung ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-12: mtha' btsal bar 'dod pa ni nam mkha' tshad gzung ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-13: mtha' btsal bar 'dod du zad do //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-15: kun dga' bo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni tshad med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-16: kun dga' bo ngas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la tshad ma bstan pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-18: tshig mang po dang 'bru mang po la ni tshad ma dang 'brel pa yod kyi /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-19: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la ni tshad ma dang 'brel ba med do zhes bya ba ni byang chub chen po thob par byed pa'i rgyu gsum pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-20: 'di dag gis ni rgyu gsungs pa yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-23: bcom ldan 'das ci'i slad du shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la tshad ma dang 'brel pa ma mchis pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-24: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:100b-25: kun dga' bo mi zad pa'i phyir shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la tshad ma dang 'brel pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-26: kun dga' bo dben pa'i phyir shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la tshad ma dang 'brel pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:100b-27: kun dga' bo 'das pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig byung ba de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyin las byung yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zad par ma gyur to //
T03TD3790.3E:101a-0: kun dga' bo ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig 'byung ba de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid las byung yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zad par 'gyur ba @101a * //
T03TD3790.3E:101a-2: kun dga' bo da ltar phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams na de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang ji snyed cig bzhugs shing 'tsho skyong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-3: chos ston pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyid las byung yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ma zad do //
T03TD3790.3E:101a-5: kun dga' bo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zad par bya bar sems pa de ni nam mkha' zad par bya bar sems su zad de /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-6: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni ma zad mi zad zad par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:101a-7: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-8: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-9: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-10: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:101a-11: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa ni ma zad mi zad zad par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:101a-14: phyi nang stong pa nyid dang /

T03TD3790.3E:148b-24: 'dus ma byas ni sangs rgyas dang sangs rgyas kyi nyan thos 'phags pa thams cad kyi don kyang yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:148b-25: phan pa'am gnod par nye bar gnas pa ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:148b-27: nam mkha'i de bzhin nyid ni gang la yang phan pa'am gnod par nye bar gnas pa ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-0: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' @149a * //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-1: chen po'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yang chos gang la yang phan pa'am gnod par nye bar gnas pa ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-3: bcom ldan 'das 'o na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos 'dus ma byas kyi shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la bslabs shing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob pa mi bgyid dam /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-7: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo 'di la bslabs shing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-8: gnyis kyi tshul gyis ma yin no zhes bya ba ni nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin la kun du rmongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-12: gnyis su ma mchis pa'i chos kyis gnyis su ma mchis pa'i chos thob par bgyid dam /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-16: 'o na gnyis kyi chos shig gnyis kyi chos thob par bgyid pa lags sam /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-22: nam gnyis kyi chos sam gnyis su med pa'i chos kyang mi dmigs pa na thob par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-24: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar gnyis kyi chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-25: gnyis su med pa'i chos mi dmigs par 'gyur ba lags /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-27: dmigs su med pa la gzugs dmigs su med cing thob pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-31: rnam par shes pa dmigs su med cing thob pa med do zhes bya ba ni gnyis su med pa la kun du rmongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-32: 'di dag gis ni 'dzin pa'i rtog pa gnyis pa dgu gsungs pa yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:149a-34: // / de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:149a-35: bcom ldan 'das shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni zab bo //
T03TD3790.3E:149b-0: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang bla na med @149b pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu zhugs pa yang dka' ba bgyid pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-2: sems can du gdags pa gang yang mi dmigs na /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-3: de dag ni sems can rnams kyi slad du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par zhugs so //
T03TD3790.3E:149b-4: bcom ldan 'das 'di lta ste dper na skyes bu la la zhig nam mkha' gzhi ma mchis pa la ljang bu bskyed par 'tshal ba de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyang sems can rnams kyi slad du rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'tshal lo //
T03TD3790.3E:149b-5: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-8: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang sems can rnams kyi phyir bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-9: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas sems can rnams sems can du 'dzin pa las yongs su 'grel ba ni dka' ba byed pa'o zhes bya ba ni dngos po med pa la dmigs pa'i ye shes ni rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-11: // / rab 'byor 'di lta ste dper na skyes bu la la zhig ni ljang bu bskyed par 'dod la /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-12: skyes bu des ljang bu de'i rtsa ba ma dmigs /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-17: 'bras bu ma dmigs par ljang bu de'i sdong bu skyed de /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-18: dus dus su chus bran zhing de'i sdong bu de rim gyis yal ga phun sum tshogs par gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-19: lo ma phun sum tshogs par gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-20: me tog phun sum tshogs par gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-21: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs par gyur pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-22: de ljang bu de'i 'dab ma la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-23: me tog la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-24: 'bras bu la spyod pa de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyang sems can rnams kyi phyir bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par 'jug ste /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-25: de dag rim gyis pha rol tu phyin pa drug la spyod cing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:149b-26: de dag lo ma dang me tog dang 'bras bu ltar sems can thams cad nye bar 'tsho bar 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:150a-1: 'byor de la lo ma ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la brten zhing sems can rnams ngan song gsum las yongs su sgrol ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:150a-2: me tog ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la brten zhing rgyal rigs che zhing mtho ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-3: bram ze'i rigs che zhing mtho ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-4: khyim bdag gi rigs che zhing mtho bar skye ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-5: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris kyi lhar skye ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-24: 'du shes med pa'i sems can dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-30: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-31: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-32: cung zad med pa'i skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-33: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched kyi lhar skye ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:150a-34: 'bras bu ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob nas sems can de dag rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la rab tu 'god pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-35: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-38: rang byang chub la rab tu 'god pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-39: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de nyid la brten zhing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-40: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob nas sems can thams cad la 'bras bus brjid par 'gyur ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-41: de la gang gis yon phul ba de dag kyang rim gyis 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-43: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:150a-45: theg pa gsum po de dag gis yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150b-0: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar @150b 'gyur yang de la sems can du'ang mi 'dogs /
T03TD3790.3E:150b-1: sems can du gdags pa'ang med par sems can de dag kyang sems can du 'dzin pa las yongs su 'grel pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:150b-2: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod kyang gang gi don du bdag gis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par bya'o zhes bya ba'i sems can nam sems can du gdags pa gang yang mi dmigs so //
T03TD3790.3E:150b-4: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du rig par bya'o //

T03TD3790.3E:150b-12: lam gyi rgyud dma' ba thams cad rgyun chad par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:150b-13: 'dod pa'i khams thams cad rgyun chad par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:150b-14: gzugs kyi khams thams cad rgyun chad par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:150b-15: gzugs med pa'i khams thams cad rgyun chad par 'gyur ro //

T03TD3790.3E:150b-19: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du rig par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:150b-20: rab 'byor gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po med na 'das pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:150b-22: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyang yod par mi 'gyur /

T03TD3790.3E:150b-28: sems can dmyal ba thams cad kyang rgyun chad par mi 'gyur /

T03TD3790.3E:151a-5: gzugs kyi khams thams cad dang /

T03TD3790.3E:151a-7: rab 'byor de bas na gang 'di skad du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du rig par bya'o zhes zer ba ni /
T03TD3790.3E:151a-10: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du rig par bya'o //

T03TD3790.3E:151a-13: de bzhin nyid gang gis rang sangs rgyas su gdags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:151a-14: de bzhin nyid gang gis 'phags pa thams cad du gdags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:151a-15: de bzhin nyid gang gis gzugs su gdags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:151a-16: de bzhin nyid gang gis tshor ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:151a-19: rnam par shes par gdags pa dang /

T03TD3790.3E:151b-0: de bzhin nyid gang gis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi @151b bar du gdags pa dang /

T03TD3790.3E:151b-4: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de ni de bzhin nyid de la bslabs shing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par byed pas /

T03TD3790.3E:151b-18: sems can rnams kyi don byed cing sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byad do //

T03TD3790.3E:152a-0: @152a * // rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par byas shing chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro //

T03TD3790.3E:152a-3: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos yon tan dang legs pa thams cad mthong nas bdag gis kyang bla na med pa yang dag pa rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed par bya'o //

T03TD3790.3E:160b-27: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar la spyod pa de la chos gang yang tshogs su 'gyur ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:160b-34: rnam par byang bar 'gyur ba gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:160b-36: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i byang chub ni chos gang yang tshogs su 'gyur ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:160b-42: kun nas nyon mongs par bya ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:160b-43: rnam par byang bar bya ba'i phyir de dmigs pa'i tshul gyis nye bar gnas par bya ba ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:160b-45: bcom ldan 'das de ltar gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i byang chub ni chos gang yang tshogs su 'gyur ba'am /

T03TD3790.3E:161a-0: rnam par byang bar bgyi ba'i slad du dmigs pa'i tshul gyis nye bar gnas @161a * //
T03TD3790.3E:161a-2: bcom ldan 'das 'o na de ji ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /

T03TD3790.3E:161a-4: ji ltar tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:161a-5: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-6: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-7: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-8: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su 'dzin par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-9: ji ltar nang stong pa nyid la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-10: ji ltar dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-11: ji ltar dran pa nye bar gzhag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-12: yang dag par spong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-16: byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-17: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-18: ji ltar 'phags pa'i bden pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-21: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-23: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-29: gzungs kyi sgo la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-30: ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-32: so so yang dag par rig pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-33: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-34: ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu la spyod par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-35: ji ltar nyan thos kyi sa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-36: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las 'da' bar 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-37: ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'i skyon ma mchis par 'jug par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-38: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-39: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la ni gnyis su spyod pa'i blo med de /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-40: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni gnyis kyis sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:161a-41: gnyis kyis tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-42: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161a-43: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-0: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa @161b dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:161b-1: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod do //

T03TD3790.3E:161b-4: gnyis kyis dran pa nye bar gzhag pa dang /

T03TD3790.3E:161b-16: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-22: gzungs kyi sgo la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:161b-23: gnyis kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs dang /

T03TD3790.3E:161b-26: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:161b-27: gnyis kyis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:161b-29: bcom ldan 'das gal te de ltar gnyis kyis sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:161b-30: gnyis kyis tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-31: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-32: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-33: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-34: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-35: gnyis kyis stong pa nyid thams cad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-36: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun la mi spyod /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-37: gnyis kyis 'phags pa'i bden pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-40: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-42: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-48: gzungs kyi sgo la mi spyod /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-49: gnyis kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-51: so so yang dag par rig pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-52: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa la mi spyod /
T03TD3790.3E:161b-53: gnyis kyis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar la mi spyod na /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-0: 'o na de ji ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam @162a * //
T03TD3790.3E:162a-1: par spyod pa de dag 'phel bar 'gyur bas sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-2: sems slad ma bskyed pa'i bar du dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par 'phel bar 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-4: rab 'byor su gang gnyis la spyod pa de dag ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnam par 'phel bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:162a-6: rab 'byor byis pa so so'i skye bo thams cad ni gnyis la brten pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-7: de dag ni dge ba'i rtsa bas rnam par mi 'phel lo //
T03TD3790.3E:162a-8: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni gnyis la mi spyod de /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-9: de ni sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-10: sems phyi ma bskyed pa'i bar du dge ba'i rtsa bas rnam par 'phel te /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-11: de ni lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyis mi dge ba'i rtsa ba gang gis nyams smad pas nyan thos kyi sa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-12: rang sangs rgyas kyi sar lhung bar 'gyur ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-13: mi dge ba'i chos gzhan gyis yongs su phrogs par gyur cing de dag gis yongs su phrogs pas sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod na /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-14: dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-15: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-16: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-17: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-18: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-19: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-20: nang stong pa nyid la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-21: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-22: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-23: yang dag par spong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-27: byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-28: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-32: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162a-34: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-0: gzungs kyi sgo la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos @162b rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-3: so so yang dag par rig pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-4: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-5: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar la spyod na dge ba'i rtsa ba mang pos rnam par mi 'phel pa de ltar nyams smad par mi nus te /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-6: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos de ltar shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyad par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:162b-9: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi slad du shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyad par bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-11: rab 'byor de ni ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:162b-12: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi phyir shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:162b-13: mi dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi phyir yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la mi spyod de /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-15: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams yongs su rdzogs par ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-16: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis yongs su ma bzung bar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:162b-18: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur bgyis pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-19: dge ba'i rtsa bas yongs su bzung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-20: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis yongs su bzung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ba lags /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-22: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-23: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur byed /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-24: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gis mdo dang /
T03TD3790.3E:162b-33: chos rmad du byung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-2: gtan la phab pa bstan pa gang ci gsungs kyang de dag thams cad yongs su 'dzin to //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-3: yongs su bzung nas kyang tshig gis yongs su 'dris pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-4: yid kyis shin tu brtags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-5: lta bas rab tu khong du chud par byas shing gzungs rab tu thob par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-6: gzungs rab tu thob nas so so yang dag par rig pa rab tu bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-7: so so yang dag par rig pa bskyed pas de'i tshe rnam par 'phos kyang chos de dag rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par gyur gyi bar du nam yang chud za bar mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-8: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dag la dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed cing /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-9: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag gis yongs su bzung na nam yang ngan song dang mi khom par skye bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-10: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag gis kyang lus yongs su dag pa yongs su 'dzin te /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-11: lus de dag gis kyang sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byed do sems can rnams yongs su smin par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-12: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag gis yongs su bzung bas dge ba'i bshes gnyen sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-13: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-14: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa pa'i legs pa ston pa dag dang nam du yang 'bral bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-15: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur bar bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-16: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bskyed par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-17: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams la brten par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-18: de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:163a-19: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la yang bsnyen bkur mi bgyid /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-20: dge ba'i rtsa ba yang yongs su rdzogs par mi bgyid la /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-21: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis kyang yongs su bzung bar ma gyur na /
T03TD3790.3E:163a-22: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par mi 'gyur ram /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-0: bcom ldan 'das kyis @163b bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-1: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang gis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-2: dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su rdzogs par ma byas la dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis yongs su ma bzung bar rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ba med do //
T03TD3790.3E:163b-4: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur yang byas /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-5: dge ba'i rtsa ba yang yongs su rdzogs par byas dge ba'i bshes gnyen la yang brten par byas kyang da dung rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par mi nus na /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-6: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-7: dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su rdzogs par ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-8: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la ma brten pa rnams rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ba lta ci smos te /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-10: rab 'byor de lta bas na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byang chub sems dpa'i ming bden pa la gnas par 'dod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-11: myur du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'dod pas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163b-12: dge ba'i rtsa ba mang po bskyed par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163b-13: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:163b-15: bcom ldan 'das ci'i slad du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur bgyis /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-17: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten par bgyis kyang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-19: de ni thabs mkhas pa dang mi ldan pa'i phyir te /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-20: des sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag las thabs de thob par ma gyur pa'i phyir dge ba'i rtsa ba de lta bu yang ma bskyed /
T03TD3790.3E:163b-21: gang de la thabs ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen de lta bu de dag la'ang ma brten pas de ltar thob par mi 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni dge 'dun dkon mchog la log par rtog pa yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-0: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po @164a * //
T03TD3790.3E:164a-1: thabs mkhas pa gang dang ldan pas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ba'i thabs mkhas pa de gang lags /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-3: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-4: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la nye bar spyod na rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang ldan pa'i yid la bya bas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-7: mi dang mi ma yin par gyur pa dag la sbyin pa yongs su gtong ba de rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang ldan pa'i yid la bya ba de dang ldan pas sbyin pa la yang sbyin pa'i 'du shes su mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-8: len pa la yang len pa'i 'du shes su mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-9: gtong ba la yang gtong ba'i 'du shes su mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:164a-10: de ni 'di ltar chos thams cad rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong par shes shing chos thams cad med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-12: yongs su ma rdzogs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-13: mngon par ma grub par mthong zhing chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid la 'jug na yang chos thams cad ni nus pa gang yang med pa'o zhes bya bar 'du byed pa med pa'i mtshan nyid kyis 'jug ste /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-14: de thabs mkhas pa de lta bu dang ldan pas na dge ba'i rtsa bas rnam par 'phel bar sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod de /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-15: de sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing sems can rnams yongs su smin par byed /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-16: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byed kyang gzhan du na sems can thams cad yongs su bskyab ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-17: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par bya ba'i phyir sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa ma gtogs par sbyin pa'i 'bras bu gang 'khor bar yongs su spyad par bya ba de lta bu'i 'bras bu la smon pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:164a-18: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-19: sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-20: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid dang ldan pa'i yid la bya bas tshul khrims bsrungs te /
T03TD3790.3E:164a-21: de la 'dod chags kyi sems sgrib par mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:164b-1: gti mug sgrib par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:164b-2: bag la nyal ba sgrib par mi 'gyur /

T03TD3790.3E:177b-32: bral ba yang ma yin pas /

T03TD3790.3E:177b-34: 'di ni de dag gi chos 'dul ba yin pas de'i phyir 'phags pa'i chos 'dul ba zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:177b-36: de ni 'di ltar chos de dag thams cad ni gzugs med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:177b-40: 'di ltar mtshan nyid med pa ste ;
T03TD3790.3E:177b-41: de dag ni gzugs med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:177b-42: gzugs med pa dang ldan pa yang ma yin /
T03TD3790.3E:177b-43: bral ba yang ma yin no //

T03TD3790.3E:177b-50: // / rab 'byor 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi gzugs med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:178a-2: mtshan nyid gcig pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa ste /

T03TD3790.3E:178a-4: des de la bslabs nas chos kyi mtshan nyid gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur ro //

T03TD3790.3E:178a-10: rnam par shes pa'i mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /

T03TD3790.3E:178a-40: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa'i mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-0: stong pa nyid dang mtshan ma @178b med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-1: smon pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-3: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-6: gzungs kyi sgo rnams kyi mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /

T03TD3790.3E:178b-13: sdug bsngal 'phags pa'i bden pa'i mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-16: lam 'phags pa'i bden pa'i mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-17: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba lugs dang mthun pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-18: lugs dang mi mthun pa'i mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-19: 'du byas kyi khams kyi mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi'am /

T03TD3790.3E:178b-21: bcom ldan 'das gal te chos 'di dag gi mtshan nyid la bslab par mi bgyi na /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-22: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid la bslabs te /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-24: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las 'da' bar 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-25: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las ma 'das na ji ltar byang chub sems dpa'i skyon ma mchis par 'jug par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-26: byang chub sems dpa'i skyon ma mchis par ma zhugs na /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-27: ji ltar rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-28: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ma thob na /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-29: ji ltar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bgyi /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-30: chos kyi 'khor lo ma bskor na ji ltar nyan thos kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-31: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-32: theg pa chen pos sems can rnams 'khor ba las sgrol bar bgyi /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-33: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-34: rab 'byor gal te chos la la zhig la mtshan nyid yod na ni de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos mtshan nyid de la bslab par yang 'gyur na /
T03TD3790.3E:178b-35: chos thams cad la mtshan nyid med cing gzugs med pa /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-1: 'di ltar mtshan nyid med par mtshan nyid gcig pas na /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-2: de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos mtshan nyid la yang bslab par mi bya /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-3: mtshan nyid med pa la yang bslab par mi bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-5: sngan chad mtshan nyid med par gyur ba de phyis mtshan nyid yod par 'gyur ba ma yin gyi /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-6: rab 'byor chos 'di dag ni sngan chad kyang mtshan nyid med la /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-7: de ltar yang mtshan nyid med pas na de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos mtshan nyid la yang bslab par mi bya /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-8: mtshan nyid med pa la yang bslab par mi bya'o//
T03TD3790.3E:179a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-11: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ma byung yang rung ste mtshan nyid med pa'i dbyings 'di ni de bzhin du gnas pa'o zhes bya ba ni mtshan nyid la log par rtog pa yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-14: bcom ldan 'das gal te de ltar chos thams cad la mtshan nyid ma mchis shing mtshan nyid tha dad pa yang ma lags /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-15: mtshan nyid gcig pa yang ma lags na /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-16: de ji ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa mchis par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-17: bcom ldan 'das shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa ma mchis par ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos nyan thos kyi sa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-18: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las 'da' bar mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-19: nyan thos kyi sa'am rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las ma 'das par ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos byang chub sems dpa'i skyon ma mchis par 'jug par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-20: byang chub sems dpa'i skyon ma mchis par ma zhugs par ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa skye bar mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-21: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa ma skyes par ni mngon par shes pa sgrub par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-22: byang chub sems dpa'i mngon par shes pa ma bsgrubs par ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par bgyi ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:179a-23: sems can yongs su smin par bgyi bar mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179a-24: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-0: sems can yongs su smin par ma bgyis par ni rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob @179b par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-1: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par ma bgyis par ni chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-2: chos kyi 'khor lo ma bskor bar ni sems can rnams rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la dgod par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-3: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-5: dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu la dgong par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-6: rang byang chub la dgod par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-7: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la dgod par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-8: sems can rnams sbyin pa las byung ba'i bsod nams bgyi ba'i dang po la dgod par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-9: tshul khrims las byung ba'i bsod nams bgyi ba'i dngos po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-10: bsgom pa las byung ba'i bsod nams bgyi ba'i dngos po la dgod par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-14: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni mtshan nyid med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-15: mtshan nyid tha dad pa'ang ma yin /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-16: mtshan nyid gcig pa'am ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-18: de ji ltar chos thams cad mtshan nyid ma mchis na ji ltar shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-20: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sgom pa ni mtshan nyid tha dad pa yang ma yin /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-21: mtshan nyid gcig pa yang ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-22: rab 'byor mtshan nyid med pa sgom pa ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:179b-24: de ji ltar na mtshan nyid ma mchis pa sgom pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-25: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:179b-26: chos thams cad rnam par sgom pa rnam par 'jig pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa'o //

T03TD3790.3E:211a-4: nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa thams cad rnam pa thams cad du rgyas par bkang zhing nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
