T03TD3790.3E:211a-6: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-7: cung zad med pa'i skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-8: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched la nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-9: de bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa de la gnas shing rnam par thar ba brgyad la lugs dang mthun pa dang lugs dang mi mthun par snyoms par 'jug cing rnam par ldang ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-10: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-11: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-12: mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-13: smon pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-14: bar chad med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-15: glog lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-16: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-17: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-18: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun la nye bar bsgrubs te gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-19: de ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di la gnas nas lam gyi rnam pa shes pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis lam gyi rnam par shes pa nyid kyi khongs su ting nge 'dzin thams cad chud par byas shing dkar po rnam par mthong ba'i sa las 'da'o //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-20: dkar po rnam par mthong ba'i sa las 'das nas rigs kyi sa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-24: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i sa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-25: byas pa rtogs pa'i sa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211a-26: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las 'da'o //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-27: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las 'das nas byang chub sems dpa'i skyon med par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-28: byang chub sems dpa'i skyon med par zhugs nas sangs rgyas kyis yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:211a-29: des de dag la spyod cing rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi ye shes ma thob kyi bar du 'bras bu bar ma dor thob par mi byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-0: ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di la gnas shing mngon par shes pa rnams yongs su rdzogs par byas nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams @211b la bsnyen bkur byed cing sangs rgyas kyi zhing nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'gro ste /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-1: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag la bsnyen bkur byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-2: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag la yang dge ba'i rtsa ba gang gis sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par 'gyur ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-3: sems can rnams yongs su smin par 'gyur ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba skyed par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-4: 'jig rten gyi khams nas 'jig rten gyi khams su 'gro zhing sems can rnams kyi don byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-5: de la sems can la la ni sbyin pas yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-6: la la ni tshul khrims kyis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-7: la la ni bzod pas yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-8: la la ni brtson 'grus kyis yongs su 'dzin to //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-9: la la ni ting nge 'dzin gyis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-10: la la ni shes rab kyis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-11: la la ni rnam par grol bas yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-12: la la ni rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong bas yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-13: la la ni rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-14: la la ni lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-16: dgra bcom pa nyid la rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-17: la la ni rang byang chub la rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-18: la la ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-19: de de ltar dge ba'i chos gang dang gang gis sems can rnams mthong bar 'gyur ba de dang de la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-20: de ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa de la gnas shing gzungs kyi sgo thams cad mngon par sgrub po //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-21: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi rab tu thob bo //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-22: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i mngon par shes pa rnams kyang thob pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-23: de nam yang las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis ma'i mngal du skye bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-24: nam yang 'dod pa la brten par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-25: sems can yongs su smin par bya ba'i don du skye ba yongs su mi 'dzin pa'ang gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-26: skye ba'i nyes pas kyang gos par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:211b-28: de ni 'di ltar des sgyu ma lta bu'i chos thams cad rab tu mthong rab tu rig rab tu rtogs pas na de sgyu ma lta bu'i 'du byed thams cad rig par byas shing snying rje chen pos yongs su bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:211b-29: sems can thams cad kyi don byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-0: de la yang sems can nam sems can @212a * //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-1: du gdags pa dmigs su med do //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-2: des chos thams cad mi dmigs nas 'jig rten gyi tha snyad nye bar bzung ste dmigs su med pa de nyid la sems can rnams 'god de /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-3: don dam par ni ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-4: de ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di la gnas shing bsam gtan dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-7: snyoms par 'jug pa thams cad la spyod de /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-8: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyi bar du nam yang ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang bral bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-9: ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di dag la gnas shing lam gyi rnam pa shes pa nyid kyis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid mngon par bsgrubs te /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-10: de la gnas nas bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor ba'i nyon mongs pa thams cad rab tu spong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:212a-11: de la gnas shing bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor ba'i nyon mongs pa thams cad rab tu spangs nas /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-14: des bdag dang gzhan gyi don byas nas lha dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-15: mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyi rim gro'i gnas su gyur pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-16: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-17: chos thams cad mtshan ma med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-18: mtshan ma dang bral ba'i sems kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do zhes bya ba ni sbyin pa la sogs pa gang yang rung bar zag pa med pa'i chos thams cad skad cig ma gcig gis bsdus pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems kyi skad cig ma gcig pa'i mngon par rtogs pa ste dang po'o /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-21: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-22: mtshan ma med pa'i chos rnams la gnas nas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ba lags /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:212a-24: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-0: yang dag pa'am yongs su grub pa'i chos gang yang yang dag par rjes su mthong ba med @212b de ;
T03TD3790.3E:212b-1: gzugs kyi yang dag pa dang yongs su grub pa yang dag par rjes su mi mthong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:212b-5: rnam par shes pa'i yang dag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-6: yongs su grub pa yang dag par rjes su mi mthong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:212b-7: de de ltar rtogs pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-8: gzugs kyi rang bzhin mi dmigs so ;
T03TD3790.3E:212b-12: rnam par shes pa'i rang bzhin mi dmigs so //
T03TD3790.3E:212b-13: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar gyi rang bzhin mi dmigs so //
T03TD3790.3E:212b-14: de shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyi pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-15: chos thams cad dngos po med pa'i rang bzhin du rtogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-16: de de ltar rtogs par byed cing nang stong pa nyid la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-17: phyi stong pa nyid la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-18: phyi nang stong pa nyid la spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-19: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-28: pha rol tu phyin pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-29: stong pa nyid thams cad dam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-30: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-34: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-35: rnam par thar pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-36: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-39: smon pa med pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-40: mngon par shes pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-43: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-45: so so yang dag par rig pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-48: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-49: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi bar ram /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-50: chos gang la yang mngon par chags pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:212b-51: de dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-52: byang chub kyi lam yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-53: 'di ltar pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-54: stong pa nyid thams cad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:212b-55: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-3: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-4: rnam par thar pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-5: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-12: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-14: so so yang dag par rig pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-17: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-18: skyes bu mi chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-19: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu yongs su 'dzin to //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-20: de byang chub sems dpa'i lam rnam par smin pa'i chos can la gnas pas pha rol tu phyin pa drug po yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-21: stong pa nyid thams cad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-22: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213a-23: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i mngon par shes pa lnga'i bar du yongs su rdzogs par gyur nas sems can gang la sbyin pas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang sbyin pas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-24: gang la tshul khrims kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang tshul khrims kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-25: gang la bzod pas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang bzod pas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-26: gang la brtson 'grus kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang brtson 'grus kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-27: gang la ting nge 'dzin gyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang ting nge 'dzin gyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-28: gang la shes rab kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang shes rab kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-29: gang la rnam par grol bas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang rnam par grol bas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-30: gang la rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong bas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la yang rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong bas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-31: gang rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la 'god par bya ba de dag kyang rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:213a-32: gang lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-3: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu 'god par bya ba de dag kyang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:213b-4: de bzhin du rgyas par sbyar bar bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:213b-5: de rdzu 'phrul gyi rnam pa du mas rnam par 'phrul zhing 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed du 'gro ste /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-6: de 'dod na 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed po de dag rin po che gang las 'dod pa'i rin po che de dag las grub par mngon par sgrub ste /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-7: de sems can rnams kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs par byed cing 'jig rten gyi khams nas 'jig rten gyi khams su 'gro ste /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-8: des 'jig rten gyi khams de dag mthong nas ci 'dod par sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su 'dzin te /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-10: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha'i ris kyi longs spyod dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-11: skyid pa lta bu dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-12: sangs rgyas kyi zhing gzhan btsal ba dang bral ba dag na longs spyod dang skyid pa gang ji snyed pa de dag der 'byung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-13: de rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-14: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-15: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-16: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-17: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-18: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-19: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i mngon par shes pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-20: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i byang chub kyi lam des lam gyi rnam pa shes pa nyid la spyod cing chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa thob nas /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-21: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid rjes su thob ste /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-22: gal te ji tsam du gzugs yongs su gzung ba med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-26: rnam par shes pa yongs su gzung ba med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:213b-29: rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba yongs su gzung ba med pa dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:213b-34: zag pa dang bcas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-0: 'dus ma byas kyi chos rnams yongs su gzung ba med pa de bzhin du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par @214a * //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-1: rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing der longs spyod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-2: skyid pa thams cad yongs su gzung ba med par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-4: de ltar chos thams cad ni dmigs su med pa'i tshul gyis yongs su gzung ba med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-5: chos thams cad yongs su gzung ba med pa'i phyir yang sems can rnams la chos ston to //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-6: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-7: chos thams cad mtshan ma med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-11: mngon par 'du bya ba med pa la shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-12: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-13: chos thams cad mtshan ma med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-17: mngon par 'du bya ba med pa la pha rol tu phyin pa rnams yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-18: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa'i bar du yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni rnam par smin pa'i chos nyid kyi gnas skabs kyi zag pa med pa'i chos thams cad skad cig gcig gis rtogs pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems kyi skad cig gis mngon par rtogs pa ste gnyis pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-19: de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:214a-20: bcom ldan 'das de ltar chos thams cad dbyer ma mchis shing mtshan ma ma mchis pa rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong pa nyid lags na /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-21: ji ltar pha rol tu phyin pa drug po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-22: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-23: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-24: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-25: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-26: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-27: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-28: zag pa dang bcas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-29: zag pa med pa'i chos de dag kyang ji ltar na tha dad du gyur par gdags pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:214a-30: ji ltar na shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin par sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa 'dus pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-0: ji ltar na shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin @214b par tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-1: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-2: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-3: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'dus pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-4: ji ltar na shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin par sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa rnams kyi bar du 'dus pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-5: bcom ldan 'das de ltar mtshan ma ma mchis pa'i chos mtshan nyid gcig pa 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-6: mtshan nyid med pa rnams la 'di ltar tha dad du byed pa dag rab tu 'byed pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-7: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor la 'di skad cis bka' stsal to //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-9: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-10: rmi lam lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la gnas shing sbyin pa yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-22: dri za'i grong khyer lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-23: sprul pa lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la nye bar gnas shing sbyin pa yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-30: nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga ni rmi lam lta bu ste /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-32: nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga ni sgyu ma lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-38: dri za'i grong khyer lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:214b-42: rmi lam la rang bzhin gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-50: sprul pa la rang bzhin gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-51: gang la rang bzhin med pa de la mtshan nyid med de gang la mtshan nyid med pa de ni 'di ltar mtshan nyid med par mtshan nyid gcig pa'o zhes bya bar rtogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:214b-52: rab 'byor rnam grangs des na khyod kyis /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-1: sbyin pa ni mtshan nyid med pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-2: gtong ba ni mtshan nyid med pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-3: len pa ni mtshan nyid med pa'o zhes bya bar shes par bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-4: gang de ltar shes nas sbyin pa gtong ba de ni sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-5: de sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed na /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-6: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa las phyir mi ldog go //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-7: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-8: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-9: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-10: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa las phyir mi ldog go //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-11: de pha rol tu phyin pa drug po de dag la gnas shing bsam gtan bzhi yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-13: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-14: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-15: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-16: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-19: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-20: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-22: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar du yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-23: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-24: mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-25: smon pa med pa ting nge 'dzin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-26: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-27: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-31: so so yang dag par rig pa rnams dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:215a-32: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215a-36: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs par byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:215a-37: de 'phags pa'i chos 'jig rten las 'das pas thun mong ma yin pa rnam par smin pa las byung ba rnams la gnas shing phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams tshad med pa grangs med dpag tu med pa dag na sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gang ji snyed cig bzhugs pa de dag gi drung du rdzu 'phrul gyis song zhing na bza' dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-1: yo byad mang pos bsnyen bkur byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-2: longs spyod dang skyid pa thams cad kyis kyang sems can rnams kyi don byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-3: de na sems can gang sbyin pas yongs su bsdu ba de dag kyang //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-4: sbyin pas yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-5: gang tshul khrims kyis yongs su bsdu ba de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-6: gang bzod pas yongs su bsdu ba de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-7: gang brtson 'grus kyis yongs su bsdu ba de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-8: gang bsam gtan gyis yongs su bsdu ba de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-9: gang shes rab kyis yongs su bsdu ba de dag kyang shes rab kyis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-10: gang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar gyis yongs su bsdu ba de dag kyang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-11: de ltar gang dang gang dge ba'i chos gang dang gang gis yongs su bsdu ba de dag kyang dge ba'i chos de dang de dag gis yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-12: de dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag dang ldan zhing chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur bas 'khor ba de nye bar len kyang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis mi gos te /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-13: de sems can rnams kyi don du mi dang lha'i phun sum tshogs pa nye bar len te /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-14: phun sum tshogs pa de dag gis sems can rnams yongs su sdud do //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-15: de chos thams cad mtshan nyid med par shes pas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu shes kyang de la mi gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-16: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-18: dgra bcom pa nyid shes kyang de la mi gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-19: rang byang chub shes kyang de la mi gnas so //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-21: 'di ltar nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad dang thun mong ma yin pa'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par bya ba'i phyir te /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-22: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-23: chos thams cad mtshan nyid med par shes pas pha rol tu phyin pa drug mtshan nyid med par shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-24: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du mtshan nyid med par shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:215b-25: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:215b-26: rmi lam lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la gnas /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-2: sprul pa lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la gnas shing tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:216a-3: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de yang nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga rmi lam lta bur shes /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-10: dri za'i grong khyer lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-11: sprul pa lta bur shes nas tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa mtshan nyid med pa ma zhig pa /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-21: lam gyi khongs su chud pa /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-23: yongs su rdzogs par byed do /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-24: de la gnas shing yang dag par blang ba'i brda dang ldan pa'i tshul khrims dang chos nyid kyis thob pa'i tshul khrims dang /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-28: mi spyad pa'i tshul khrims bsrung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:216a-29: de tshul khrims de lta bu dang ldan yang 'dis bdag rgyal rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu che zhing mtho ba'i rigs dang skal ba mnyam pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-30: bram ze'i rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu che zhing mtho ba'i rigs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-31: khyim bdag gi rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu che zhing mtho ba'i rigs dang skal ba mnyam par skye bar bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-33: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por 'gyur bar bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-34: rgyal chen bzhi'i rigs kyi lha rnams dang skal ba mnyam par skye bar bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-39: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha rnams dang skal ba mnyam par skye bar bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-44: 'og min gyi lha rnams dang skal pa mnyam par skye bar bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216a-45: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu thob par bya'o zhe'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-0: @216b byang chub thob par bya'o zhes tshul khrims des mchog tu 'dzin pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-2: 'di ltar chos thams cad ni mtshan nyid med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-3: 'di ltar dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi mtshan nyid du mtshan nyid gcig pas na mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyis mtshan nyid med pa'i chos thob par mi rung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-4: mtshan nyid tha dad pa'i chos kyis mtshan nyid tha dad pa'i chos thob par mi rung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-6: mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyis kyang mtshan nyid tha dad pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-7: mtshan nyid med pa'i chos thob par mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-8: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa mtshan nyid med pa yongs su rdzogs par byas nas byang chub sems dpa'i skyon med par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-9: byang chub sems dpa'i skyon med par 'jug pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-10: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob ste /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-11: lam gyi rnam pa shas pa nyid la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-12: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i mngon par shes pa lnga rab tu thob nas /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-13: gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-14: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo lnga brgya la gnas te /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-15: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi thob nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la bsnyen bkur byed cing /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-16: sangs rgyas kyi zhing nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'gro ste /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-17: sems can rnams kyang yongs su smin par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-18: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su 'dzin to //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-19: de 'gro ba lnga'i 'khor ba na 'khor yang 'khor ba'i las kyi rnam par smin pas gos par mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-20: 'di lta ste dper na sprul pa ni 'gro ba 'am 'ong ba'am sdod pa'am 'dug pa'am nyal bar byed kyang de la 'gro ba'am 'ong ba'am sdod pa'am 'dug pa'am nyal ba yang mi dmigs te /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-21: de sems can rnams kyi don yang byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:216b-22: sems can dang sems can du gdags pa yang mi dmigs so /
T03TD3790.3E:216b-24: // / bam po drug cu lnga pa /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-0: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas shin tu zhi ba zhes bya ba bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te sems can tshad med pa theg pa gnyis @217a * //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-1: kyis yongs su mya ngan las 'das kyang gang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung bstan par bya ba'i byang chub sems dpa' de lta bu gang yang ma gzigs nas des tshe'i 'du byed spangs nas sprul pa sprul pa mdzad de /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-2: phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-3: rab 'byor de ltar sprul pa des bskal pa gcig lon nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung bstan te yongs su mya ngan las 'das par gyur to //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-4: yongs su mya ngan las 'das par gyur pa de'i gzugs sam /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-9: dngos po gang yang dmigs su med do //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-10: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po yang sems can nam sems can du gdags par mi dmigs la sems can rnams kyi don kyang byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-11: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-12: mtshan nyid med pa'i tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-13: de yongs su rdzogs pas mtshan nyid med pa'i chos thams cad khong du chud par shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-14: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-15: rmi lam lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la gnas /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-20: sprul pa lta bu'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la gnas te /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-21: mtshan nyid med pa'i bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:217a-23: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po mtshan nyid med pa'i nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga po rnams la gnas nas bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par bgyid pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-24: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:217a-25: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bzod pa gnyis kyis bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-0: @217b nyams su len pa'i bzod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-1: chos khong du chud pa'i bzod pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:217b-2: de la nyams su len pa'i bzod pa gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-3: sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-4: snying po byang chub la 'dug gi bar du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i drung du gal te sems can thams cad yang dang yang du 'ongs shing gshe ba'am mi snyan par brjod cing ma klas pa'i tshig brlang bar zer bar gyur tam /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-5: rdo dbyug dang mtshon chas brdegs sam btab kyang de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs par 'dod pas /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-6: sems bskyed pa 'ga' tsam yang 'khrugs pa dang ldan pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-7: gnod sems dang ldan pa bskyed par mi bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-8: phyir sems can de dag la kye ma sems can 'di dag ni nyon mongs pa'i nad kyis mnar ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-9: 'di dag la bdag gis sdig to'i sems mi bskyed kyi /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-10: 'di ni bdag nyid kyis phung po dgrar gyur pa 'di rnams blangs pas lan to zhes de dag la lhag par snying rje bskyed par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:217b-11: byams pa dang ldan te snying rje bar gyur nas rnam pa de ltar rtogs pa de ni nyams su len pa'i bzod pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:217b-12: de la chos khong du chud pa'i bzod pa gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-13: sems can de dag kyang don dam par dmigs su med na /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-16: ma klas pa'i tshig brlang po zer ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-17: rdo dbyug gis brdeg cing mtshon 'debs pa lta bu zhig yod de /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-18: 'du byed thams cad ni sgyu ma lta bu gsob gsog rag las pa nam mkha' lta bu /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-19: bdag dang sems can dang srog dang /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-25: shed bdag dang bral ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-26: rnam par rtog pa de dag thams cad ni yongs su rtog pa las byung ba yin na /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-28: mi snyan par brjod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-29: ma klas pa'i tshig brlang po zer ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-30: rdo dbyug gis brdeg cing mtshon 'debs pa lta bu zhig yod de /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-31: bdag gis ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-32: don dam pa stong pa nyid nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:217b-33: de ltar rnam par brtag par mi bya'o zhes bya ba 'di ni chos khong du chud pa'i bzod pa zhes bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-0: de de ltar yongs su rtog cing bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa @218a * //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-1: yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-2: de bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs pa des mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-4: bcom ldan 'das mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa zhes bgyi ba ni gang lags /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-5: de la spangs pa ni ci mchis ye shes ni ci mchis /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-7: rab 'byor chos gang la yang rdul tsam yang skye ba med pa de ni mi skye ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-8: de gang gis shes pa de ni bzod pa zhes bya ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-9: shes pa des mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa 'thob po //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-11: bcom ldan 'das nyan thos rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-12: rang sangs rgyas rnams kyi mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa gang lags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-13: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa gang lags pa'i bzod pa de dag la bye brag tu bgyi ba ci mchis /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-15: rab 'byor rgyun du zhugs pa'i shes pa gang yin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-16: spong ba gang yin pa de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bzod pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-17: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i shes pa gang yin pa dang spong ba gang yin pa de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bzod pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-18: phyir mi 'ong ba'i shes pa gang yin pa dang spong ba gang yin pa de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bzod pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-19: dgra bcom pa'i shes pa gang yin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-20: spong ba gang yin pa de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bzod pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-21: rang sangs rgyas kyi shes pa gang yin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-22: spong ba gang yin pa de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bzod pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-23: rab 'byor de ni nyan thos dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-24: rang sangs rgyas kyi bzod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-25: byang chub sems dpa'i bzod pa'i bye brag yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:218a-26: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de ni bzod pa de lta bu dang ldan pas nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas de dag thams cad zil gyis gnon te /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-27: de rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i mi skye ba'i chos gyi [*kyi] bzod pa la gnas te /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-28: byang chub sems dpa'i lam la spyod cing lam gyi rnam pa shes pa nyid yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:218a-29: de yongs su rdzogs pas byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-2: smon pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams dang mi 'bral ba yin /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-3: de mngon par shes pa rnams dang mi 'bral ba yin /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-4: de mngon par shes pa rnams dang mi 'bral bas sems can rnams yongs su smin par byed pa yin /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-5: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su rdzogs par byed pa yin ;
T03TD3790.3E:218b-6: de sems can rnams yongs su smin par byas /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-7: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byas nas /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-8: skad cig gcig dang ldan pa'i shes rab kyis rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:218b-9: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /

T03TD3790.3E:226a-26: thabs mkhas pas sems can ser sna can de dag ser sna las rnam par bzlog nas sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor te sbyin pa yongs su btang ba de yang de dag la longs spyod chen po'i rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:226a-27: des de dag las bskyod nas tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-28: tshul khrims yang dag par blangs pa de yang de dag la mtho ris su skye ba'i rgyur 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:226a-29: des de dag las bskyod nas ting nge 'dzin la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-30: ting nge 'dzin de yang de dag la tshangs pa'i 'jig rten du skye ba'i rgyur 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:226a-31: des de dag las bskyod nas bsam gtan dang po la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-32: bsam gtan dang po las bsam gtan gnyis pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-33: bsam gtan gnyis pa las bsam gtan gsum pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-34: bsam gtan gsum pa las bsam gtan bzhi pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-35: bsam gtan bzhi pa las nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226a-36: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa las rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-0: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa las cung zad med pa'i skye mched kyi snyoms @226b par 'jug pa /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-1: cung zad med pa'i skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa las 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa la sbyor ro //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-2: des sbyin pa dang sbyin pa'i 'bras bu dma' ba de las rnam grangs su bskyed de /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-3: phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su dbugs 'byin to //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-6: de tshul khrims dang tshul khrims kyi 'bras bu de las rnam grangs du mas bskyed de /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-7: phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-8: des ting nge 'dzin dang ting nge 'dzin gyi 'bras bu de las rnam grangs du mas bskyed de /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-9: phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su rab tu gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-10: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-11: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-12: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-15: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-16: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-20: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-21: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-22: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-23: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-24: mngon par shes pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-27: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-29: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:226b-32: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-34: de zag pa med pa'i chos gzugs med pa bstan du med pa thogs pa med pa de dag gis gang rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu don du gnyer ba de dag rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-35: gang lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu don du gnyer ba de dag lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-36: gang phyir mi 'ong ba'i 'bras bu don du gnyer pa de dag phyir mi 'ong ba'i 'bras bu la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:226b-37: gang dgra bcom pa nyid don du gnyer ba de dag dgra bcom pa nyid la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-0: gang rang byang chub don du gnyer pa de dag rang byang @227a * //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-2: gang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub don du gnyer ba de dag la byang chub kyi lam brjod cing ston to //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-4: yang dag par gzengs bstod do //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-5: yang dag par dga' bar byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-9: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-10: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-17: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-18: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong pa la rnam par 'god par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-19: de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-20: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-21: bcom ldan 'das de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo 'di la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-22: chos thams cad dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-23: chos thams cad mtha' las 'das pa stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-24: thog ma dang tha ma med pa stong pa nyid la 'di dag ni dge ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-25: 'di dag ni mi dge ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-26: 'di dag ni 'jig rten pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-27: 'di dag ni 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-28: 'di dag ni kha na ma tho ba dang bcas pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-29: 'di dag ni kha na ma tho pa med pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-30: 'di dag ni zag pa dang bcas pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-31: 'di dag ni zag pa med pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-32: 'di dag ni 'dus byas kyi chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-33: 'di dag ni 'dus ma byas kyi chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-34: 'di dag ni rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-35: 'di dag ni lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-37: dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-38: 'di dag ni rang byang chub kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-39: 'di dag ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'o zhes bya bar rnam par dgod par bgyid pa de dag ni ngo mtshar te rmad du byung ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227a-40: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227a-41: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-2: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo 'di nyid la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-3: chos thams cad dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-4: chos thams cad mtha' las 'das ba stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-5: thog ma dang tha ma med pa stong pa nyid la 'di dag ni dge ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-6: 'di dag ni mi dge ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-7: 'di dag ni 'jig rten pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-8: 'di dag ni 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-9: 'di dag ni kha na ma tho ba med pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-10: 'di dag ni zag pa dang bcas pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-11: 'di dag ni zag pa med pa'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-12: 'di dag ni 'dus byas kyi chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-13: 'di dag ni 'dus ma byas kyi chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-14: 'di dag ni rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-15: 'di dag ni lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-17: dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-18: 'di dag ni rang byang chub kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-19: 'di dag ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'o zhes bya bar rnam par dgod par byed pa de ni ngo mtshar te rmad du byung ba'i chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-20: rab 'byor gal te khyod kyis byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang gi ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos de shes kyang nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de la slar phan gdags par bya ba sla ba ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-21: khyed cag thams cad kyis kyang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i chos de dag zil gyis mnan par mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-23: bcom ldan 'das nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad la ma mchis pa'i ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ma mchis pa gang lags /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-24: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-25: rab 'byor de'i phyir shin tu legs par nyon la yid la zung shig dang bshad par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:227b-26: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:227b-27: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug la gnas /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-0: rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i stong pa nyid thams cad @228a * //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-2: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-6: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-7: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-8: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-15: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-17: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-20: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad la gnas shing phyogs dang phyogs mtshams kyi 'jig rten gyi khams dag tu song zhing sems can gang la sbyin pas phan gdags par bya ba de ni sbyin pas phan gdags so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-21: de sems can gang la tshul khrims dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-25: shes rab kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni shes rab kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-26: sems can gang la bsam gtan dang po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-29: bsam gtan bzhi pas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni bsam gtan bzhi pas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-30: sems can gang la nam mkha' mtha' yas kyi skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-31: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-32: cung zad med pa'i skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-33: 'du shes med 'du shes med min gyi skye mched kyi snyoms par 'jug pas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched la snyoms par 'jug pas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-34: sems can gang la byams pas phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni byams pas phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-35: sems can gang la snying rje dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:228a-37: btang snyoms kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni btang snyoms kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228a-38: sems can gang la dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-39: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228a-40: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-0: byang chub kyi yan lag @228b bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-1: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-3: rnam par thar ba brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-4: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-11: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-13: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-16: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad kyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la ni sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228b-17: gang la rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar gyis phan gdags par bya ba de dag la rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyis phan 'dogs so //
T03TD3790.3E:228b-19: bcom ldan 'das ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pas sems can rnams la phan 'dogs pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-21: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-24: bzhon pa 'dod pa rnams la bzhon pa /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-25: phreng ba 'dod pa rnams la phreng ba /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-27: byug pa 'dod pa rnams la byug pa /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-29: mal cha 'dod pa rnam la mal cha /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-31: mi'i yo byad gang ci yang rung ba'i par du yongs su gtong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-32: ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la dbul zhing yongs su gtong pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-33: ji ltar rang sangs rgyas rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-36: lan cig phyir 'on ba rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-37: rgyun du zhugs pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-38: yang dag par spong pa rnams dang ;
T03TD3790.3E:228b-39: yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la yongs su gtong ba de bzhin du mir gyur pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:228b-40: de bzhin du byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa'i sems can thams cad la yang tha dad du bya ba med pa'i 'du shes nye bar gzhag cing sbyin pa yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-1: chos thams cad ni tha dad du bya ba med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-2: des tha dad du bya ba med pa'i sbyin pa byin pas tha dad du bya ba med pa'i chos 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-3: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid thob par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-4: rab 'byor gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa'i srog chags sbyin pa'i gnas ma yin pa mthong nas /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-5: 'di snyam du bdag gi sbyin gnas ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-6: byol song gi skye gnas su gtogs pa ma yin no snyam na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i chos ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-8: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos ni byang chub tu sems bskyed nas 'di ltar bdag gis sems can 'di dag la ni sbyin pas phan gdags par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-9: 'di dag la ni phan gdags par mi bya'o zhes bya bar bla na med pa yan dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par zhugs pa ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-10: de dag sbyin pas phan btags nas rgyal rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu'i rigs su skye /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-11: bram ze'i rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu'i rigs su skye /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-12: khyim bdag gi rigs shing s'a la chen po lta bu'i rigs su skye bar 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-13: sbyin pa de nyid kyis phan btags pa de dag theg pa gsum gyis rim gyis phung po ma lus pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-14: gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po la skye bo'i tshogs thams cad kyis bsad par gsol ba btab na /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-15: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sbyin no snyam pa'am ;
T03TD3790.3E:229a-16: mi sbyin no snyam pa'i sems gzhan bskyed par mi bya'i /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-17: 'khrug pa med pa'i sems kyis skye bo'i tshogs de dag la sbyin par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229a-19: 'di ltar de ni sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par zhugs pa'i phyir /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-20: gal te rnam par rtog na sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-21: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de dag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:229a-25: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyis smad par 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-0: de la @229b thog mar sems can thams cad kyi mgon gyis shig ce'am /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-1: gnas dang skyabs dang dpung gnyen gyis shig ces gsol ba btab ces smad par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-2: rab 'byor gzhan yang gal te byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i drung du mir gyur pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-3: mi ma yin par gyur pa dag 'ongs nas bdag ni slong mo pa'o zhes yan lag bcad par gsol ba btab na de'i tshe des sbyin nam mi sbyin snyam pa'i sems gnyis su bskyed par mi bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-5: de ni 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des sems can rnams kyi don du ched du bsams te /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-6: lus 'dis bdag gis sems can thams cad kyi don bya'o zhes lus yongs su bzung bas na de 'di snyam du bdag gis sems can 'di dag gi don du lus yongs su bzung bas na de dag blang mi dgos par khyer cig dengs shig ces sems bskyed par bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-7: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la bslab par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-8: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos slong mo pa mthong na 'di snyam du chos 'di dag thams cad kyi rang bzhin dmigs su med na /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-9: 'di la su zhig ni sbyin pa yongs su gtong /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-10: su la ni sbyin par bya /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-11: ci zhig ni sbyin par bya zhes sems bskyed par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-13: 'di ltar chos 'di dag ni mtha' las 'das pa stong pa nyid kyis stong pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-14: stong pa nyid la ni gang la yang yongs su stong pa'am gang las kyang phrogs pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-15: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyi pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:229b-16: 'di lta ste nang stong pa nyid nas dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar la bslab par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:229b-17: de stong pa nyid la ngas shing sbyin pa yongs su gtong ba de'i sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur te /

T03TD3790.3E:234b-0: @234b rab 'byor de ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos so //

T03TD3790.3E:240b-30: chos dang nye bar chos la nan tan du byed na yang des de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes par mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:240b-32: thugs yeng yeng por mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:240b-33: 'di ni dgongs pa nye bar gzhag pa dang po'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-0: la la rna ba btud de rim gror nyan zhing bka' @241a * //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-1: nyan pa'i sems nye bar gzhog pa med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-2: chos dang gnyer ba'i chos nan tan du mi byed na yang des de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs khro bar mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-4: thugs mi ches par mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-5: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa nye bar gzhag pa gnyis pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-6: la la rna ba btud de rim gror nyan zhing bka' mnyan pa'i sems nye bar gzhog la chos dang gnyer ba'i chos la nan tan du byed /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-7: la la rna ba btud de rim gror mi byed cing /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-8: bka' mnyan pa'i sems nye bar gzhog pa med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-9: chos dang gnyer ba'i chos nan tan du mi byed kyang /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-10: des de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-11: thugs khro bar gnyis su mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-12: thams cad du dgongs pa dang ldan zhing mkhyen par btang snyoms su rnam par spyod pa 'di ni dgongs pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-13: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyams pa med pa'i chos nyid gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-14: gang gis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams don yod pa'i chos ston pa'i phyir /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-15: sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad pa la dus las mi 'da' ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-16: de ni nyams pa med pa'i chos nyid ces bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-17: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i bag chags kyi sgrib pa rab tu spangs pa gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-18: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad ni nyon mongs pa spangs kyang lus kyi 'gyur ba yod kyi /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-19: de bzhin gshegs pa la ni de lta bu yang mi mnga' ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-20: de ni bag chags kyi sgrib pa rab tu spangs pa zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-21: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje chen po gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-22: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje chen po gang dang ldan pas 'jig rten gyi brda nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-23: dge ba'i rtsa ba gzigs pa'i phyir dus thams cad du 'jig rten la nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du rtog pa mdzad ces bya ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-24: dngos su na sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi thugs rje chen po sems can mtha' yas pa yongs su smin par bya ba la gzigs pa rtag par 'byung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241a-25: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje chen po zhes bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241a-26: rab 'byor de bzhin gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-0: de bzhin @241b gshegs pa la 'khrul pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-2: dgongs pa nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-4: thugs mnyam par ma bzhag pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-5: so sor ma brtags pa'i btang snyoms mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-6: mos pa yongs su nyams pa mi mnga' //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-7: brtson 'grus yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-8: dran pa yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-9: ting nge 'dzin yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-10: shes rab yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-11: rnam par grol ba yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-12: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa yongs su nyams pa mi mnga'o ;
T03TD3790.3E:241b-13: / sku'i phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-14: ye shes kyi rjes su 'brang ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-15: gsung gi phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-16: ye shes kyi rjes su 'brang ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-17: thugs kyi phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-18: ye shes kyi rjes su 'brang ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-19: 'das pa'i dus la ma chags ma thogs pa'i ye shes gzigs pa 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-20: ma 'ongs pa'i dus la ma chags ma thogs pa'i ye shes gzugs pa 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-21: de ltar byung ba'i du la ma chags ma thogs pa'i ye shes gzigs pa 'jug ste /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-22: de dang ni sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa rnams so //
T03TD3790.3E:241b-23: rab 'byor de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-24: gang la dmigs pa med pa dran pas dbang bsgyur ba zhi ba'i rnam pa dang ldan pa mtshan nyid med pa'i mtshan nyid ni rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ces bya'o /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-26: // / bam po drug cu bdun pa ;
T03TD3790.3E:241b-27: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-28: phyag dang zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-29: zhabs shin tu gnas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-30: phyag dang zhabs dra bas 'brel pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-31: phyag dang zhabs gzhon zhing 'jam pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-32: bdun shin tu mtho ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-35: sku che zhing drang ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-36: zhabs legs par mtho ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-37: yan lag gi spu gyen du 'khyil pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-38: ri dgas ae na ya'i byin pa lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-39: phyag brla drang por slebs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:241b-40: gsang ba'i gnas sbubs su nub pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-1: spu re re nas g-yas phyogs su 'khyil pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-2: zhal mdzod spus brgyan pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-3: seng ge'i ro stod lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-4: phrag pa'i lhun mdzes par grub pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-5: phrag so shin tu rgyas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-7: shing n+ya gro dha ltar chu zheng gab pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-8: dbu spyi gtsug dang ldan pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-9: ljags shin tu yangs pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-11: seng ge'i 'gram pa lta bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-12: tshems shin tu dkar ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-13: tshems shin tu mnyam pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-15: tshems mnyam zhing bzhi bcu tshang ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-17: ba'i rdzi ma lta bu ste /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-18: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil la 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-19: mu khyud can lte ba dang bcas pa rnam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-21: ba so la gzugs su brkos pa dang 'dra ba mnga' bas phyag dang zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldang pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-22: zhabs kyi mthil gnyis mnyam par sa la 'jog cing zhabs sum pa med pas zhabs shin tu gnas pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-23: ngang pa'i rgyal po ltar phyag dang zhabs kyi sor mo ring bas 'brel pas phyag dang zhabs dra bas 'brel ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-24: shing bal gyi sgo nga ltar shin tu 'jam zhing gzhon pas phyag dang zhabs gzhon zhing 'jam pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-25: phyag dang zhabs dang mgur gyi lhun shin tu mtho bas bdun shin tu mtho ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-26: phyag dang zhabs kyi sor mo ring bas sor mo ring ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-27: rting pa ring bas rting pa yangs pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-28: sku khru bdun du 'phags la drang bas sku che zheng drang ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-29: bus mo'i lha da dang long bu mdzes par nub pas zhabs legs par mtho ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-30: spu gyen du g-yas phyogs su 'khyil pas yan lag gi spu gyen du 'khyil ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-31: ri dgas ae na ya'i byin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242a-32: smyig ma dang ldum bu dar ba ltar drang zhing ma nyams la rim gyis gzhol bar grub cing byin pa zlum pas ri dgas ae na ya'i byin pa lta bu'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242a-33: brla drang por bzhag ste ma btud kyang phyag gi mthil gnyis kyis pus mo'i lha nga la reg pas phyag brla drang por slebs pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-0: glang po dang rta cang shes ltar gsang ba'i gnas shin tu mdzes shing sbubs su @242b nub pas gsang ba'i gnas sbubs su nub pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-1: shin tu sbyangs pa'i gser gyi kha dog lta bu dang ldan pas gser gyi kha dog go //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-2: gser dang dngul shin tu sbyangs pa ltar 'jam zhing gzhon pa'i mdog tu 'dug la sku la rdul gyis mi 'go bas kha dag shin tu 'jam pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-3: shin tu rnam par phye ba'i spu re rer skyes shing gnyis su med pas spu re re nas g-yas phyogs su 'khyil pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-4: me tog kun da dang zla ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:242b-6: ba mo'i mdog ltar 'dug pa nyi ma dang zla ba brgya las kyang 'phags par 'od gsal ba'i mdzod spus smin mtshams shin tu brgyan pas zhal mdzod spus brgyan pa'o ;
T03TD3790.3E:242b-7: / ro stod tshe bas seng ge'i ro stod do //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-8: mgur dang rgyud legs par 'brel zhing lhun zlum pas phrag pa'i lhun mdzes par grub pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-9: gser gyi gtan pa shin tu phyis pa la phrag so legs par grub pas phrag so shin tu legs par rgyas pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-10: rlung dang mkhris pa dang bde kan gyis ma nyams shing rnam par shes pa 'dra ba med pas ro bro ba'i mchog go //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-11: sku chu zheng 'dom du mnyam pas shing n+ya gro dha ltar chu zheng gab pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-12: spyi gtsug zlum zhing legs la g-yas phyogs su 'khyil pa dang ldan pa'i dbu mnyam zhing legs par grub la mdzes pa mnga' bas dbu spyi gtsug dang ldan pa'o ;
T03TD3790.3E:242b-13: / me tog autpala dmar po'i 'dab ma'i mdog ltar 'dug cing shin tu yangs pas ljags shin tu yangs shing srab pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-14: tshangs pa dang bya ka la ping ka lta bu'i gsung mnga' bas tshangs pa'i dbyangs so //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-15: 'gram pa me long gi dkyil 'khor ltar legs par grub cing mdzes par skyes te /
T03TD3790.3E:242b-16: yid du 'ong bas seng ge'i 'gram pa lta bu'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-17: me tog kun da dang dung gi bcag 'phro ltar shin tu dkar ba'i tshems mnga' bas tshems shin tu dkar ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-18: tshems la mtho dman med pas tshems mnyam pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-19: tshems la mtshams ma dod pas tshems thags bzang ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-20: bla 'og dgye gu med pas tshems mnyam zhing bzhi bcu tshad ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-21: dkar nag gi cha ma 'dres la shin tu rnam par dag cing mdog dmar pos ma g-yogs pas spyan dkar nag 'byes pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:242b-22: rdzi ma bla 'og tu legs par gnas la ma 'dzing pas ba'i rdzi ma lta bu'o //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-0: de la bla ma la bsu skyel @243a * //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-2: chos nyan ba la bstod pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-4: mchod rten la sogs pa'i bsti stong byas pas phyag dang zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-5: da ni 'khor shin tu mnga' ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-6: yid dam la brtan pas zhabs shin tu gnas pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-7: de ni mi g-yo zhing shin tu brtan pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-11: don mthun pa'i bsdu ba rnam pa bzhi goms par byas pas /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-12: phyag dang zhabs dra bas 'brel pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-13: de ni myur du 'du ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-14: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang btung ba zhim zhing nyams su bde ba byin pas phyag dang zhabs gzhon zhing 'jam pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-15: bdun shin tu mtho ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-16: de gnyis ni bza' ba dang btung ba zhim zhing nyams su bde ba thob pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-18: srog gi rim gro byas pa dang srog gcod pa spangs pas /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-20: rting pa yangs pa dang sku che zhing drang ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-21: de ni sku tshe ring ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-22: dge ba'i chos yang dag par blangs pa dang bzung ba mngon par spel zhing 'grib par ma byas pas zhabs kyi gong mtho ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-23: yan lag gi spu gyen du 'khyil pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-24: de ni mi nyams pa'i chos dang ldan pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-25: rig pa dang bzo'i las la rim gror byas shing gzhan la byin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-26: bdag gis blangs pas ri dgas ae na ya'i byin pa lta bu ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-27: de ni myur du 'dzin pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-28: bdog cing yod pa'i nor la bslangs nas mi god par gtong zhig med ces ma byas pas phyag brla drang por slebs pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-29: de ni yo byad la dbang ba dang dul ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-30: 'grogs pa dang mdza' ba shes dang gnyen pa ma phye ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-31: dbyi bar gyur pa'i sems can rnams tshangs pa'i spyod pa la yang dag par bskul ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-32: gsad ba'i tshig yongs su bsrungs pas gsang ba'i gnas sbubs su nub pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-33: de ni bu mang ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243a-34: stan dang gos dang khang pa dang gzhal med khang dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-35: gnas bzang po byin pas gser gyi kha dog dang mdog shin tu 'jam pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-36: de gnyis ni gdan dang na bzang dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243a-37: khang pa dang gzhal med khang ngang gnas bzang po 'thob pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-3: phu nu la sogs pa bla ma rnams la tshul dang 'dra bar rim gro byas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-5: bsgo ba rnal ma gzan pas spu re re nas g-yas phyogs su 'khyil pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-6: zhal mdzod spus brgyan pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-7: de ni mnyam pa med pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-8: mi snyan pa mi zer zhing mi smod pa snyan par smra zhing legs par bshad pa mthun par 'dzin pas seng ge'i ro stod lta bu dang phrag pa'i lhun mdzes par grub pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-9: de ni thub pa med pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-10: na ba rnams la rtsis dang rim gro dang sman dang nyams su phan pa'i zas byin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-11: rim gror byas pas phrag so shin tu rgyas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-13: de ni nad nyung ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-17: rgal dka' ba'i za pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-20: stegs dang gtsug lag khang bya ba la sogs pa la gzhan mos par bya ba sngon du gtong zhing bdag gis gzhan la byin pas shing n+ya gro dha ltar chu zheng gab pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-21: dbu spyi gtsug dang ldan pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-22: de ni mnga' chen po mnga' ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-23: yun ring por tshig snyan zhing 'jam pa dang nyams su bde bar smras pas ljags shin tu yangs shing srab pa dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs te /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-24: de gnyis ni yan lag lnga dang ldan pa'i gsung mnga' ba'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-25: gsung yan lag lnga dang ldan pa zhes bya ba ni /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-26: yongs su shes shing rnam par shes par 'gyur ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-27: mnyan na dga' zhing mi mthun pa med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-28: zab cing dbyangs rjes su 'byung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-29: btang mi bra zhing rnar snyan pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-31: yun ring po nas tshig 'khyal pa spangs shing dus su smra smra bas seng ge'i 'gram pa lta bu ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-32: de ni tshigs kun gyis snyan pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-33: rim gror bya ba dang brnyas pa med pa gnyis kyis 'tsho ba yongs su dag pas tshems shin tu dkar ba dang mnyam pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-34: de ni 'khor snga nas bsags pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:243b-35: yun ring po nas bden zhing phra ma med pa'i tshig smra smra bas tshems thags bzang ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-36: tshems mnyam zhing bzhi bcu tshang ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:243b-37: de ni 'khor dbyer mi phyed pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:244a-0: pang gis 'khyud pa bzhin du nyes par bsam @244a * //
T03TD3790.3E:244a-1: pa med pa la ma chags shing mi sdang ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-2: rmongs pa med pa'i mig gis lta lta bas spyan dkar nag 'byes pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-3: ba'i rdzi ma lta bu ste de ni kun nas mdzes pa'i snga ltas so //
T03TD3790.3E:244a-4: rab 'byor de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i mi chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
T03TD3790.3E:244a-5: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu gang zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-7: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni mngon par 'du bya ba thams cad las dben pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-8: sen mo zangs kyi mdog ltar 'dug pa yin /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-9: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni gnyen bshes byams pa dang 'dra bar sems can la phan pa dang bde ba'i thugs mnga' ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-10: sen mo mdog snum pa yin /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-11: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni rigs dang rgyud mthon por byung ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-13: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni tshul kha na ma thob mi mnga' ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:244a-15: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni dge ba'i rtsa ba shin tu tshogs pa ste /

T03TD3790.3E:264b-26: thabs mkhas pas sems can rnams la chos kyi dbyings ston to //

T03TD3790.3E:264b-29: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:264b-30: de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:264b-31: bcom ldan 'das de ltar gal te sems can yang shin tu dmigs su ma mchis la /

T03TD3790.3E:265a-1: don du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sgom pa lags /
