T03TD3790.3E:287a-29: de de ltar sbyin pas yongs su bsdus pa'i sems can de yang rim gyis tshul khrims la rab tu dgod do //
T03TD3790.3E:287a-33: shes rab la rab tu dgod do //
T03TD3790.3E:287a-36: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi la rab tu dgod do //
T03TD3790.3E:287a-37: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287a-38: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287a-39: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287a-42: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287a-43: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-3: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-4: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-5: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-6: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-9: mngon par shes pa lnga dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-11: gzungs kyi sgo rnams la rab tu 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-12: yang dag pa'i skyon med par 'jug par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-13: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-14: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-16: dgra bcom pa nyid thob par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-17: rang byang chub thob par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-18: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-19: kye skyes bu dag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub ni mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar mi dka' ste /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-20: phyin ci log gis rmongs pa'i sems can rnams kyi khong du mi chud pa ma gtogs par chos gang la sems can rnams chags par gyur pa'i chos de lta bu gang yang ngo bo nyid kyis yod pa med kyis /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-21: phyin ci log gi 'dzin pa thams cad rgyun chod la 'khor ba las bdag kyang thar bar gyis shig / gzhan yang thar par gyis shig / de ltar khyed cag kyang don chen po gyis shig / gzhan yang don chen po la sbyor cig ces yang dag par skul bar byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-22: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyad par bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-23: de ltar spyod pa'i tshe ci nas kyang sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-24: nam yang ngan song du mi ltung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-25: nam yang 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po mi byed par mi 'gyur ba de ltar spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:287b-27: sa bon ji lta ba bzhin du 'bras bu 'byung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-28: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po de'i drung du slong mo pa gang ji snyed cig 'ongs kyang /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-29: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po de 'di snyam du sems te /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-30: bdag gis sems can rnams kyi don ma gtogs par gzhan du na 'khor los sgyur ba yongs su ma bzung ngo zhes de 'di skad ces zer te /
T03TD3790.3E:287b-31: su ci 'dod pa de khyod la byin gyis 'di ni nga'i ma yin gyi khyed kyi'o //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-0: nga ni nang gi gzugs la yang don du gnyer @288a * //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-3: gzhan du na ngas sems can rnams kyi don du 'khor ba yongs su bzung gi / bdag gi don du ni 'khor ba don du gnyer ba ma yin no zhes te /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-4: de snying brtse bas snying rje chen po yongs su rdzogs bar byas shing snying rje chen pos sems can rnams kyi don byed kyang sems can gang yongs su grub pa de lta bu mi dmigs te /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-6: ming dang tha snyad kyis rnam par spyod de /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-7: rnam par spyod pa de yang sgra brnyan lta bur rnam par spyad du med par shes so //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-8: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la de ltar spyad par bya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-9: spyod pa'i tshe ci nas kyang bdag gi sha yan chad kyang sems can rnams la yongs su ma btang ba med par bya na /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-10: phyi rol gyi yo byad gang gis sems can rnams 'khor ba las yongs su thar bar bya ba dag lta smos su yang med pa de ltar spyad par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-12: bcom ldan 'das yo byad de dag gang lags /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-14: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-15: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-16: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-17: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-18: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-19: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-20: nang stong pa nyid ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-21: phyi stong pa nyid ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-22: phyi nang stong pa nyid ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-23: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-24: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-25: yang dag par spong ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-29: byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-30: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-34: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-36: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-42: gzungs kyi sgo rnams ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288a-43: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288a-45: so so yang dag par rig ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-0: sangs rgyas @288b kyi chos ma 'dres pa rnams ni yo byad do //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-1: de dag ni yo byad de /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-2: yod byad de dag gis sems can rnams yongs su bsdus shing rim gyis nyan thos kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-3: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-5: theg pa gsum po de dag gis yongs su mya ngan las zlo ste /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-6: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-7: rab 'byor ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyi pa la spyod cing sems can rnams tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor ba yin zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-8: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing sems can rnams la sbyin pa yang yongs su gtong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-9: de sbyin pa gtong ba'i tshe 'di skad ces brjod do //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-10: rigs kyi bu dag tshur shog / tshul khrims srungs shig / ngas khyed la zas dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-32: yo byad gang ci yang rung ba'i bar gyis phongs pa med par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-33: khyed kyang phongs pas tshul khrims ngan pa la spyod grang na /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-34: khyed yo byad thams cad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-35: rin po che sna bdun gyi bar gyis phongs pa med par byas /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-36: des khyed sdom pa'i tshul khrims la gnos la rim gyis nyan thos kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-37: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-38: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi theg pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:288b-39: theg pa gsum po de dag gis sdug bsngal mthar gyis shig ces nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che po de bdag nyid kyang tshul khrims bsrung so //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-40: gzhan yang tshul khrims la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-41: tshul khrims kyi legs pa brjod do //
T03TD3790.3E:288b-42: sems can gzhan gang tshul khrims bsrung ba de dag gi yang legs pa brjod cing mthun pas dga' bar spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:289a-0: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de sems can de dag @289a * //
T03TD3790.3E:289a-1: de ltar tshul khrims la sbyar zhing tshul khrims la rab tu bkod de /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-2: rim gyis theg pa gsum pos yongs su mya ngan las zlo ste /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-3: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:289a-4: rab 'byor ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing sems can rnams bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor ba yin zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-5: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing sems can gang khro ba dang gnod sems su byed pa dag mthong na /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-6: de la 'di skad ces zer ro //
T03TD3790.3E:289a-7: rigs kyi bu dag khyed ci'i rgyus gnod sems su byed par gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-8: khyed gang gis phongs shing gnod sems su byed par gyur ba de dang de nga las long shig / ngas khyed zas dang /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-10: mi'i rkyen gyi yo byad gang ci rung ba'i bar gyis phongs pa med par byas /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-11: khro ba dang gnod sems med par gyis shig ces de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing sems can de dag bzod pa la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-12: 'di skad du gcugs gnag gis khro ba skye bar gyur ba de ni snying po med pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-13: de la dngos po gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:289a-14: khro ba de ni yang dag pa ma yin par yongs su brtags pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-15: dngos po gang gi phyir khyed 'thab cing 'khon pa dang gnod sems su byed par gyur pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-16: de ltar 'thab cing 'khon te gnod sems su gyur nas dbyig pa 'gyed pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-18: phan tshun gyi srog la rgal bar 'gyur ba'i dngos po de la dngos po'i rang bzhin gang yang med na /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-19: de ltar yin yang khyed yang dag pa ma yin pa'i yongs su rtog pas 'khrugs na /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-20: sems can dmyal ba dag tu ltung bar 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-21: byol song gi skye gnas dang /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-22: gshin rje'i 'jig rten dag tu ltung bar 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-23: de ma yin pa'i ngan song gzhan dag tu yang khyed sdug bsngal mi bzad pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:289a-24: tsha zhing rtsub pa yid du mi 'ong ba'i tshor ba nyams su myong bar 'gyur gyis /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-0: skyes bu khyed rnams dngos po med pa'i chos kyi don du las gang yongs su bzung bas mir skye ba yang thob @289b par mi 'gyur na /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-1: sangs rgyas 'byung ba dang phrad par 'gyur ba lta smos su med pa de lta bu'i las yongs su ma 'dzin cig /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-2: grogs po dag sangs rgyas 'byung ba ni dkon no //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-3: mir skye ba thob pa ni dkon no //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-4: dal ba phun sum tshogs pa ni dkon no //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-5: 'khor ba las thar pa ni dkon no //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-6: de ltar yin gyi dal ba 'di ni don med par ma byed cig / mi khom par gyur cing gsor mi rung bar gyur ta re zhes de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bdag nyid kyang bzod pa sgrub bo //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-7: gzhan yang bzod pa la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-8: bzod pa'i legs pa brjod do //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-9: sems can gzhan gang bzod pa sgom pa de dag gi legs pa brjod cing mthun pas dga' bar byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-10: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de sems can de dag de ltar bzod pa la sbyar zhing bzod pa la rab tu bkod do //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-11: rim gyis theg pa gsum gyis yongs su mya ngan las zlo ste /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-12: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:289b-13: rab 'byor ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-14: sems can rnams brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor ba yin zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-15: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sems can le lo can brtson 'grus chung ba dag mthong ba na /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-16: 'di skad du khyod ci'i phyir le lo byed ces brjod de /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-17: de dag rkyen dang mi ldan pa'i phyir ro zhes zer na /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-18: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing sems can de dag la 'di skad ces zer te /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-19: kye skyes bu dag ngas sbyin pa'i rkyen tam /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-22: gzhan yang rnam pa gang dang gang gis brtson 'grus rtsom du rung ba de dag khyed la ngas nye bar bsgrub par byas /
T03TD3790.3E:289b-23: brtson 'grus rtsoms shig ces nas sems can de dag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de'i yo byad la spyod cing lus sam /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-0: de dag lus dang sems kyi brtson 'grus kyis dge ba'i chos thams @290a * //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-1: cad yongs su rdzogs par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-2: dge ba'i chos de dag gis 'phags pa zag pa med pa'i chos rnams sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-3: de dag bsgoms pas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu 'thob po //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-4: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-8: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-9: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bdag nyid kyang brtson 'grus rtsom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-10: gzhan yang brtson 'grus la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-11: brtson 'grus kyi legs pa brjod do //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-12: sems can gzhan gang brtson 'grus rtsom pa de dag gi legs pa brjod cing mthun pas dga' bar spyod do //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-13: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de sems can de dag de ltar brtson 'grus la sbyor zhing brtson 'grus la rab tu bkod do ;
T03TD3790.3E:290a-14: / rim gyis theg pa gsum pos yongs su mya ngan las zlo ste /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-15: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-16: rab 'byor ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa la sems can rnams sbyor ba yin zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-17: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sems g-yeng bar gyur pa'i sems can dag mthong na 'di skad du sems can khyed ci'i phyir bsam gtan la mnyam par mi 'jog ces brjod do //
T03TD3790.3E:290a-18: de dag rkyen dang mi ldan pa'i phyir ro zhes zer na /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-19: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing sems can de dag la 'di skad du 'dems te /
T03TD3790.3E:290a-20: kye sems can dag ngas rkyen gang dang gang gis phyi nang gi chos la rnam par rtog par mi 'gyur ba de lta bu'i rkyen nye bar bsgrub par bya'o zhes nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de sems can de dag la rkyen gang dang gang nye bar bsgrubs pas rnam par rtog par mi 'gyur ba de lta bu'i rkyen nye bar bsgrubs te /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-0: de'i phyir de dag rnam par rtog pa chad @290b nas bsam gtan dang po la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-3: bsam gtan bzhi pa la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-4: byams pa la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-7: btang snyoms la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-8: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-9: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-10: cung zad med pa'i skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-11: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-14: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa de dag gis sems 'dul bar gyur pas dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-15: yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-16: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-19: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-20: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-21: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-22: de dag bsgoms pas rim gyis theg pa gsum pos yongs su mya ngan las 'das te /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-23: de ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi lam las yongs su mi nyams te /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-24: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing ting nge 'dzin gyi pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:290b-25: rab 'byor ji ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pas sems can rnams yongs su sdud pa yin zhe na /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-26: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing shes rab 'chal bar gyur ba'i sems can dag mthong na /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-27: 'di skad du sems can khyed ci'i phyir shes rab mi sgom zhes brjod de /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-28: de dag rkyen dang mi ldan pa'i phyir ro zhes zer na /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-29: de la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing sems can de dag la 'di skad du 'dems te /
T03TD3790.3E:290b-30: nga las yo byad rnams long la sbyin pa byin cig / tshul khrims srungs shig / bzod pa bsgoms shig //
T03TD3790.3E:291a-0: brtson 'grus rtsoms shig / ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par zhog cig / rnam pa de dag yongs su rdzogs @291a * //
T03TD3790.3E:291a-2: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgom pa la bdag gam /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-23: pha rol tu phyin pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-24: stong pa nyid thams cad dam /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-25: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-29: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-31: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:291a-38: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs sam /

T03TD3790.3E:298b-28: lus kyi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:298b-29: yid kyi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba'i 'dus shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-30: sa'i khams kyi 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-35: rnam par shes pa'i khams kyi 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-36: ma rig pa'i 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-48: rga shi'i 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-49: bud med kyi 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-50: skyes pa'i 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-51: 'dod pa'i khams kyi 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-53: gzugs med pa'i khams kyi 'du shes ni gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:298b-58: zag pa dang bcas pa'i 'du shes dang /
T03TD3790.3E:298b-59: zag pa med pa'i 'du shes dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-2: rab 'byor de dag ni byang chub sems dpa'i lus kyi gnas ngan len to //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-3: ngag gi gnas ngan len dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-4: yid kyi gnas ngan len te /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-5: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-6: gnas ngan len de thams cad rnam par spangs shing bdag kyang sbyin pa yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-7: gzhan yang sbyin pa la yang dag par bskul te /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-8: de zas 'dod pa la ni zas yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-10: gos 'dod pa la ni gos yongs su gtong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-11: mi'i rkyen dang yo byad gang ci yang rung ba'i bar du 'dod pa la ni de dag yongs su gtong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-12: gzhan yang mi'i rkyen dang yo byad gang ci yang rung ba'i bar du yongs su gtong pa la yang dag par bskul zhing rab tu 'god de /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-13: de'i dge ba'i rtsa ba gang ji snyed pa de dag kyang sems can thams cad dang thun mong du byas shing sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par bya ba'i phyir yongs su bsngo'o //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-14: de bdag nyid kyang tshul khrims bsrung ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-15: gzhan yang tshul khrims la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-16: bdag kyang bzod pa sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-17: gzhan yang bzod pa la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-19: gzhan yang brtson 'grus la yang dag par bskul lo ;
T03TD3790.3E:299a-20: / bdag kyang bsam gtan la snyoms par 'jug go //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-21: gzhan yang bsam gtan la yang dag par bskul lo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-22: bdag kyang shes rab sgom mo //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-23: gzhan yang shes rab la yang dag par bskul zhing gzhog go //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-26: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag kyang sems can thams cad dang thun mong du byas shing sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par bya ba'i phyir yongs su bsngo ste /
T03TD3790.3E:299a-27: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams rin po che sna bdun gyis yongs su bkang zhing dkon mchog gsum la 'bul bar byed kyang de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing rin po che sna bdun gyi rgyu las grub par gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:299a-28: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sangs rgyas kyi spyan mnga'am /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-0: sangs rgyas kyi mchod rten gyi drung du lha rdzas kyi rol mo brdung pa dkrol bar byed kyang de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag gi @299b sangs rgyas kyi zhing du lha rdzas kyi sgra yid du 'ong ba rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad bar 'byung bar gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:299b-1: rab 'byor gzhan yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams lha rdzas kyi spos kyis yongs su bkang zhing sangs rgyas rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-2: sangs rgyas kyi mchod rten dag la 'bul bar byed kyang de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing der rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par lha rdzas kyi spos kyi ngad ldang bar gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:299b-3: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ro brgya dang ldan pa'i kha zas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-4: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyan thos la 'bul bar byed cing de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing der bdag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-5: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa la man bus brtsal ro brgya dang ldan pa mngon par 'grub par gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:299b-6: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de bzhin gshegs pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-7: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten dag la lha rdzas kyi byug pa yongs su 'bul bar byed kyang de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing de'i sems can thams cad kyang lha rdzas kyi reg pa dang ldan par gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:299b-8: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'di snyam du yid kyis bsams pa tsam gyis yid du 'ong ba'i gzugs dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-12: reg rnams sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-14: sems can thams cad la dbul zhing yongs su gtang bar bya'o snyam du sems te /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-15: de de ltar sems pa'i tshe 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag gi sangs rgyas kyi zhing der bdag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:299b-16: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-0: sems can thams cad kyang yid kyis bsams pa tsam gyis @300a * //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-5: reg yongs su 'grub par gyur cig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-6: rab 'byor gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-8: mal bdag nyid kyang bsam gtan dang po la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-9: sems can thams cad kyang bsam gtan dang po la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-10: ma la bdag nyid kyang bsam gtan gnyis pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-12: bsam gtan bzhi pa la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-13: sems can thams cad kyang bsam gtan bzhi pa la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-14: ma la bdag nyid kyang byams pa la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-15: sems can thams cad kyang byams pa la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-16: ma la bdag nyid kyang snying rje dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-18: btang snyoms la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-19: sems can thams cad kyang btang snyoms la 'god do//
T03TD3790.3E:300a-20: ma la bdag nyid kyang nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-21: sems can thams cad kyang nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-22: ma la bdag nyid kyang rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-23: cung zad med pa'i skye mched dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-24: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched la mnyam par gzhag go //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-25: sems can thams cad kyang 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-26: ma la bdag nyid kyang dran pa nye bar gzhag pa rnams bsgom par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-27: sems can thams cad kyang dran pa nye bar gzhag pa rnams la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-28: ma la bdag nyid kyang yang dag par spong pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-32: byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-33: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa bsgom par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-34: sems can thams cad kyang 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la 'god do //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-35: ma la bdag nyid kyang rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-37: smon pa med pa bsgom par bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:300a-38: sems can thams cad kyang rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-40: smon pa med pa la 'god do snyam ste /
T03TD3790.3E:300a-41: de de ltar sems pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-0: de 'di snyam du dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag bla na med pa yang @300b dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing de'i sems can thams cad bsam gtan bzhi dang mi 'bral zhing tshad med pa bzhi dang mi 'bral ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-1: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-2: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-3: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyi dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-5: smon pa med pa dang mi 'bral bar shog shig ces bya bar sems bskyed do //
T03TD3790.3E:300b-6: rab 'byor de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-7: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yong su dag par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:300b-8: de nam bsam pa de dag thams cad yongs su rdzogs par ma gyur gyi bar du bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang mi rgya ste /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-9: de bdag nyid kyang dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad dang ldan pa yin /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-10: sems can de dag thams cad kyang dge ba'i rtsa ba dang ldan par byed pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-11: de bdag nyid kyi lus kyang mdzes pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-12: sems can gang byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des yongs su smin par byas pa de dag kyang 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-13: bsod nams kyis yongs su bzung ba'i phyir gzugs bzang zhing mdzes la yid du 'ong ba'i gzugs mngon par 'grub ste ;
T03TD3790.3E:300b-14: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing de ltar yongs su dag par byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-15: ci nas kyang ngan song gsum du gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-16: lta ba'i rnam par gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-19: gti mug tu gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-21: skyes par gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-22: theg pa gnyis su gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-25: bdag med par gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-26: yongs su 'dzin par gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-27: bdag dang bdag gir bya bar gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-29: kun nas ldang bar gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:300b-30: phyin ci log tu gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-0: 'bras bur gdags pa'i ming yang mi srid cing gzhan du na @301a * //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-1: sems can de dag 'dod pa bzhin du shing rlung gis btab pa'am phyi nang gi dngos po dag las 'di lta ste /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-2: stong pa nyid kyi sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-3: mtshan ma med pa'i sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-4: smon pa med pa'i sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-5: mi skye mi 'gag pa'i sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-6: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pa'i sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-7: chos thams cad chos thams cad kyis stong pa'i sgra 'byung ba dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-8: chos de dag gi ngo bo nyid ji lta ba bzhin ngo bo nyid med pa'i sgra dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-9: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams byung yang rung /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ma byung yang rung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-11: chos thams cad chos thams cad kyis stong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-12: gang stong pa nyid de la ni mtshan ma med do //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-13: gang la ni mtshan ma med pa de la ni smon pa med do zhes bya ba'i chos bstan pa'i sgra nyin mtshan rgyun mi 'chad par 'gro yang rung /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-17: rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad pa 'byung bar 'gyur ba de lta bur sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su sbyong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-18: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing der bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas kyang de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de la phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams dag na sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gang ji snyed cig bzhugs pa de dag thams cad legs pa brjod par 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-19: sems can gang gis de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan thos pa de dag thams cad kyang bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu nges par 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-20: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas des chos bstan na /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-21: sems can gang yang 'di ni chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-22: 'di ni chos ma yin zhes bya bar the tshom za bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-24: de ni 'di ltar chos rnams kyi chos nyid gang yin pa de la ni chos ma yin pa gang yang med de thams cad kyang chos so //
T03TD3790.3E:301a-25: de la sems can gang mi dge ba'i rtsa bas non pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-27: sangs rgyas kyi nyan thos rnams la dge ba'i rtsa ba ma bskyed pa mi dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis yongs su zin pa /
T03TD3790.3E:301a-28: bdag tu lta bar bying ba nas lta ba'i rnam pa thams cad kyi bar du bying ba rtag pa'am chad pa'i mtha' la gnas pa /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-0: @301b log par 'dzin pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma yin pa la ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin par 'du shes pa /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-1: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin pa la ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma yin par 'du shes pa de dag ni chos ma yin pa yang chos so zhes zer /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-2: chos la yang chos ma yin no zhes zer ro //
T03TD3790.3E:301b-3: de dag chos spong bar 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-4: de ltar chos spangs nas lus zhig pa'i 'og tu shi nas ngan song dang /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-6: log par ltung ba sems can dmyal ba dag tu skye bar 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-7: de lta bu dag la yang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas zhing 'khor ba'i khongs su chud pa'i sems can de dag sdig par lta ba'i rnam pa de dag las rnam par 'grol te /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-8: de ltar rnam par bkrol nas nges pa'i phung por rab tu bkod do //
T03TD3790.3E:301b-9: der bkod pa rnams phyin chad ngan song du ltung bar mi 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:301b-10: rab 'byor de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par byed pa yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-11: de ltar yongs su sbyangs pas sems can rnams 'jig rten pa'i chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-13: zag pa dang bcas pa'i chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-14: zag pa med pa'i chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-16: 'dus ma byas kyi chos gang la yang gnas par mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-17: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi bar du nges par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa la 'god pa'i phrin las yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-19: // / de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:301b-20: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des zhes bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-23: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni nges pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-24: ma nges pa ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:301b-26: bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi phung po'am /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-27: rang sangs rgyas kyi phung po'am /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-29: phung po gang du nges pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:301b-30: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-0: @302a * // rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni nyan thos kyi phung por nges pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-1: rang sangs rgyas kyi phung por nges pa ma yin gyi /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-2: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni sangs rgyas kyi phung por nges so //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-4: bcom ldan 'das sems dang po bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni nges zhes bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-5: 'on tam phyir mi ldog par nges zhes bgyi /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-6: skye ba gcig gis thogs par nges zhes bgyi'am /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-7: 'on tam srid pa tha mar nges zhes bgyi /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-9: rab 'byor sems dang po bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni nges pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-10: phyir mi ldog pa ni nges pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-11: srid pa gcig gis thogs pa ni nges pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-13: bcom ldan 'das nges pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen por ngan song rnams su skye bar 'gyur ram mi 'gyur /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa ;
T03TD3790.3E:302a-15: rab 'byor de ni ma yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-16: rab 'byor nges pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni ngan song du mi skye'o //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-17: rab 'byor de ji snyam du sems /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-23: rang sangs rgyas ngan song du skye bar 'gyur ram /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-25: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma lags so //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-27: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-32: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-34: mi dge ba'i chos thams cad spang ba'i don du gnas pa de ni ngan song du skye bar 'gyur ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-35: lha tshe ring por skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-36: gang na dge ba'i chos rnams mi spyod pa de lta bur skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-37: glen pa dang lkugs par 'gyur ba'i yul du skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-39: mi srun zhing 'khor bzhi rgyur med pa'i yul du skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-40: log par lta ba'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302a-41: gang na sangs rgyas kyi sgra mi grag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:302a-42: chos kyi sgra mi grag pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-0: dge 'dun gyi sgra mi @302b grag par 'gyur ba de lta bur skye ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302b-1: bya ba ma yin par lta bar ltung ba'i gnas med do //
T03TD3790.3E:302b-2: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste /

T03TD3790.3E:302b-5: bcom ldan 'das gal te de ltar nges pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de lta bu'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang ldan zhing tshul dang mi 'dra ba'i gnas su mi skye ba lags na /

T03TD3790.3E:302b-7: de'i tshe dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag gang du mchis /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-9: rab 'byor byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni mi dge ba'i las kyis byol song gi rgyud du skye ba ma yin gyi /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-10: lus gang dang gang gis sems can rnams don du 'gyur ba de dang de lta bu'i lus ched du bsams shing sems can rnams kyi don du yongs su 'dzin kyang /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-11: rab 'byor de ni 'di ltar thabs mkhas pas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byol song gi skye gnas su skyes shing de la la zhig gsod du 'ongs kyang bla na med pa'i bzod pas bdag yongs su gtong zhing sems can de dag la gnod par mi byed pa de lta bu'i thabs mkhas pa dag dgra bcom pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-12: rang sangs rgyas dag la yod dam /

T03TD3790.3E:302b-15: bcom ldan 'das dge ba'i chos gang la gnas shing byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de lta bu'i lus yongs su 'dzin /
T03TD3790.3E:302b-16: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

T03TD3790.3E:303a-0: dge ba'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa ni bla na @303a * //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-1: med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub ste /
T03TD3790.3E:303a-2: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar bzung ste snying po byang chub la 'jug gi bar du dge ba'i chos gang yang yongs su rdzogs par mi bya ba med do //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-3: dge ba'i chos gang yang yongs su rdzogs par ma byas par bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ba de lta bu med de /
T03TD3790.3E:303a-4: de ni gnas ma yin no //

T03TD3790.3E:303a-11: byol song gi skye gnas su skye bar 'gyur /

T03TD3790.3E:303a-13: rab 'byor de bzhin gshegs pa 'phags pa zag pa med pa yin nam /
T03TD3790.3E:303a-15: bcom ldan 'das de de lags so //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-16: bde bar gshegs pa de de lags te de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'phags shing zag pa mi mnga' ba'o //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

T03TD3790.3E:303a-23: rab 'byor des de bzhin gshegs pa byol song gi skye gnas par 'gyur ram /
T03TD3790.3E:303a-25: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma lags so //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

T03TD3790.3E:303a-29: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma lags so //
T03TD3790.3E:303a-30: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-0: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' @303b sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa'i chos zag pa med pa dang ldan pa yang ched du bsams shing de lta bu'i lus yongs su 'dzin te /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-1: lus de dag gis sems can rnams ci rigs ci tshul du yongs su smin par byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:303b-2: rab 'byor de ji snyam du sems /

T03TD3790.3E:303b-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-8: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa'i chos zag pa med pa dang ldan pa yang ched du bsams shing de lta bu'i lus yongs su 'dzin te /

T03TD3790.3E:303b-10: de lta bu'i lus des sdug bsngal du yang mi 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-11: sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba yang nyams su mi myong ngo //
T03TD3790.3E:303b-12: rab 'byor de ji snyam du sems /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-13: sgyu ma'i mkhan pos sgyu ma las glang po'i gzugs sam /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-15: glang gi gzugs shig bstan tam /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-16: gzhan yang sgyu ma rnam pa sna tshogs bstan na /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-17: de dag glang po'i gzugs sam /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-20: srog chags kyi rigs gzhan dag tu yang 'gyur ba yod dam /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-22: bcom ldan 'das de ni ma mchis so //
T03TD3790.3E:303b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-24: rab 'byor de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa'i chos zag pa med pa dang ldan pa yang ched du bsams shing de lta bu'i lus yongs su 'dzin te /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-25: lus de dag gis sems can rnams kyi don byed de /
T03TD3790.3E:303b-26: sdug bsngal gyi tshor bar 'gyur ba gang yang med do //
T03TD3790.3E:303b-28: kye ma bcom ldan 'das de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa'i ye shes zag pa ma mchis pa dang ldan zhing lus gang dang gang gis sems can rnams kyi don du 'gyur ba de dang de lta bu'i lus yongs su 'dzin pa ni thabs shin tu mkhas pa ste de ni ngo mtshar che'o zhes bya ba ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la nges par 'jog pa'i phrin las yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-0: // / bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' @304a * //
T03TD3790.3E:304a-1: sems dpa' chen po ni chos dkar po gang dang gang la gnas shing de lta bu'i thabs mkhas pa bgyid kyang las de lta bus mi gos par spyod pa lags /

T03TD3790.3E:304a-7: gang gis reg par byed pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-8: gang la reg par bya ba de lta bu'i chos gsum po de dag thams cad mi dmigs te /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-10: de ni 'di ltar chos gsum po de dag thams cad ngo bo nyid kyis stong pas stong pa nyid ni stong pa nyid la reg par mi byed do //

T03TD3790.3E:304a-12: stong pa nyid kyang reg par bya ba ma yin no //
T03TD3790.3E:304a-14: de ni 'di ltar stong pa nyid la stong pa nyid mi dmigs so //
T03TD3790.3E:304a-15: de ni mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid de /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-16: de la gnas shing byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:304a-19: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po chos gzhan la mi gnas kyi /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-20: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'ba' zhig la gnas shing rnam pa de lta bu'i thabs mkhas pa la spyod pa lags sam /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-22: rab 'byor chos gang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i khongs su ma chud pa de lta bu yod dam /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-24: bcom ldan 'das gal te shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ngo bo nyid kyis stong na /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-25: ji ltar shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i khongs su chos thams cad 'dus pa lags /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-26: bcom ldan 'das stong pa nyid la ni chos gang yang khongs su chud pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-27: khongs su ma chud pa zhes bgyi ba ma mchis so //
T03TD3790.3E:304a-28: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:304a-29: rab 'byor chos thams cad chos thams cad kyis mi stong ngam /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-1: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-2: rab 'byor de ste chos thams cad chos thams cad kyis stong na /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-3: chos thams cad stong pa nyid du ma 'dus sam /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-5: bcom ldan 'das de de lags so //
T03TD3790.3E:304b-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-8: khyod kyis 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la gnas shing de lta bu'i thabs mkhas pa la spyod par rig par bya'o zhes bya ba ni sems can gyi don tshad med pa la 'god pa'i phrin las yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-10: // / de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor gyis bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
T03TD3790.3E:304b-11: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing chos thams cad stong pa nyid la gnas te /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-12: mngon par shes pa gang la gnas shing phyogs bcu'i phyogs re re'i 'jig rten gyi khams gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed dag tu mchi ba dang /

T03TD3790.3E:304b-16: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //

T03TD3790.3E:304b-20: 'jig rten gyi khams de dag na sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gang ji snyed cig bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag kyang ngo bo nyid kyis stong par mthong ngo //

T03TD3790.3E:304b-23: gal te 'jig rten gyi khams de dag kyang ngo bo nyid kyis mi stong la /
T03TD3790.3E:304b-24: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag kyang ngo bo nyid kyis mi stong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-1: kyang ngo bo nyid kyis mi stong pa zhig yin na ni /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-2: nyi tshe'i stong pa nyid du 'gyur te /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-3: de yang stong pa nyi tshe ba ma yin no /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-4: de'i phyir chos thams cad chos thams cad kyis stong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-5: de nyid kyi phyir byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po thabs mkhas pas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod cing /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-6: mngon par shes pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa mngon par bsgrubs te /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-7: mngon par shes pa de dag la gnas shing lha'i mig dang /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-10: pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-11: sngon gyi gnas dran pa dang /

T03TD3790.3E:305a-13: mngon par shes pa med par byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar mi nus so //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-15: 'di ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i byang chub ni mngon par shes pa'i pha rol tu phyin par 'dus pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-16: mngon par shes pa de dag las byang chub yongs su btsal bar bya'o //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-17: de tshol ba'i tshe lha'i mig rnam par dag pa mi las 'das pas bdag nyid kyang dge ba'i chos thams cad mthong la /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-18: gzhan yang dge ba'i chos thams cad la sbyor te /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-19: dge ba'i chos de dag la mngon par zhen par 'gyur ba med do //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-21: dge ba'i chos de dag thams cad ni ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-22: stong pa nyid ni gang la mngon par zhen cing ro myong bar byed par mngon par zhen par 'gyur ba med de /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-23: stong pa nyid ni ro myong bar byed pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-24: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa'i tshe /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-25: lha'i mig mngon par bsgrubs te /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-26: lha'i mig des chos thams cad kyang stong pa nyid du mthong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-27: de chos de dag la gnas shing las mngon par sgrub bo //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-28: las mngon par sgrub pa des sems can rnams la chos ston te /
T03TD3790.3E:305a-29: sems can nam sems can du gdags par dmigs pa med do //
T03TD3790.3E:305a-30: de ltar mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po mngon par shes pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa mngon par bsgrubs te /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-0: mngon par shes pa de dag gis mngon par shes par bya ba'i chos gang ji snyed pa de dag @305b byed do //
T03TD3790.3E:305b-1: de lha'i mig rnam par dag pa mi las 'das pa de nyid kyis shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad mthong ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-2: de dag tu rdzu 'phrul gyis song zhing sbyin pa'am /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-8: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-9: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-14: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-15: rnam par thar pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-17: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-18: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-20: so so yang dag par rig pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-21: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa rnams sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-23: rang sangs rgyas kyi chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-24: byang chub sems dpa'i chos sam /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-25: sangs rgyas kyi chos kyis sems can rnams kyi don byed cing /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-26: sems can de dag gi bya ba byed de //
T03TD3790.3E:305b-27: de la sems can ser sna can gang ji snyed pa de dag la 'di skad du chos ston te /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-28: sbyin pa byin cig / phongs pa ni sdug bsngal ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-29: phongs pas ni bdag gi don kyang mi nus na /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-30: gzhan gyi don lta ci smos kyis /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-31: de ltar khyed kyis sbyin pa byin la bdag kyang bde bar gyis shig / gzhan yang bde bar gyis shig / phongs pas zil gyis non zhing nying sha nying gis zos te /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-32: ngan song gsum las mi thar bar gyur ta re zhes chos ston to //
T03TD3790.3E:305b-33: sems can tshul khrims ngan pa can gang ji snyed pa de dag la 'di skad du chos ston te /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-34: skyes bu dag tshul khrims ngan pa ni sdug bsngal ba ste /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-35: tshul khrims ngan pas ni bdag gi don yang bya bar mi nus na /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-36: gzhan gyi don lta ci smos te /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-37: tshul khrims ngan pa'i rnam par smin pa ni sems can dmyal ba'am /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-38: byol song gi skye gnas sam ;
T03TD3790.3E:305b-40: de ltar khyed ngan song gsum du ltung na /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-41: bdag kyang gdon par mi nus na /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-42: gzhan gdon par lta ci smos kyis /
T03TD3790.3E:305b-43: de'i phyir khyed kyis tshul khrims ngan pa'i sems 'ga' tsam gyi go skabs kyang mi dbye'o //
T03TD3790.3E:306a-0: phyis 'gyod pa can du gyur ta re zhes chos @306a * //

T03TD3790.3E:310b-0: rab 'byor dge ba'i chos de dag ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi @310b lam ste /

T03TD3790.3E:310b-10: / bcom ldan 'das gal te chos de dag thams cad byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i chos lags na /

T03TD3790.3E:310b-14: sangs rgyas kyi chos gang yin zhes zer ba ni /

T03TD3790.3E:311a-6: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong pa'i chos de dag la ni sems can dmyal ba pa'o //

T03TD3790.3E:311a-37: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /

T03TD3790.3E:311b-13: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /

T03TD3790.3E:311b-44: bcom ldan 'das de ste ma dmigs na /

T03TD3790.3E:311b-47: gshin rje'i 'jig rten du ji ltar gdags par mdzad /
T03TD3790.3E:311b-48: lha dang mir ji ltar gdags par mdzad /
T03TD3790.3E:311b-53: rang sangs rgyas su ji ltar gdags par mdzad /

T03TD3790.3E:312a-3: rab 'byor ci sems can 'di dag chos rnams rang gi mtshan nyid kyis stong par shes sam ;

T03TD3790.3E:341a-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-5: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni sprul pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-6: de la la ni nyan thos kyis sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-7: la la ni rang sangs rgyas kyis sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-8: la la ni byang chub sems dpas sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-9: la la ni de bzhin gshegs pas sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-10: la la ni nyon mongs pas sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-11: la la ni las kyis sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-12: rab 'byor rnam grangs des na chos thams cad sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-14: bcom ldan 'das gang spangs pa zhes bgyi ba rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu'am /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-20: bag chags kyi mtshams sbyar ba thams cad spangs pa'i chos de dag kyang sprul pa lags sam /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-23: 'gag pa'i chos gang ci yang rung ste /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-26: bcom ldan 'das gang ma sprul pa'i chos de dag gang lags /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-27: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-28: chos gang la skye ba yang med /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-29: 'gag pa yang med pa de ni ma sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-32: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-33: mi mnyam pa'i rmongs pa med pa'i chos can gyi mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-34: chos de ni ma sprul pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-36: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'di skad du stong pa nyid las kyang mi g-yo la /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-37: gnyis su yang mi dmigs te /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-38: chos gang yang stong pa nyid ma yin pa de lta bu med do zhes bka' stsal pa de ltar na /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-39: bcom ldan 'das rmongs pa med pa'i chos can yang sprul par 'gyur ro //
T03TD3790.3E:341a-40: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-43: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni stong pa ste /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-44: de dag ni nyan thos kyis ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:341a-45: rang sangs rgyas kyis ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-0: @341b byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos ma byas /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis ma byas te /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-2: ngo bo nyid kyi stong pa nyid gang yin pa de ni mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
T03TD3790.3E:341b-4: bcom ldan 'das las dang po pa'i gang zag gis ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid yongs su 'tshal bar bgyi na ji ltar gdams shing rjes su bstan par bgyi /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-5: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-6: rab 'byor ci sngon dngos po yod par 'gyur la phyis dngos po med par gyur pa yod dam /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-7: rab 'byor 'di la dngos po yod pa yang med /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-8: dngos po med pa yang med /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-10: gzhan gyi dngos po yang med na /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-11: de la gang yongs su shes par bya ba'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid ces bya ba lta yod par 'gyur re skan zhes bya ba ni mya ngan las 'das pa la dgod pa'i phrin las yin te /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-12: 'di dag gis ni phrin las rnams gsungs so //
T03TD3790.3E:341b-13: chos kyi sku'i mngon par rtogs pa bstan zin to //
T03TD3790.3E:341b-14: 'phags pa bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-15: mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan gyi rjes su 'brangs nas dag par gtugs pa las /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-16: chos kyi sku'i dbang du byas pa bslab pa'i 'bras bu'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-18: // / bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-19: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po byams pa la sogs pa grangs med pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-20: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-21: tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-22: tshe dang ldan pa mood gal gyi bu chen po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-23: tshe dang ldan pa 'od srungs chen po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-24: tshe dang ldan pa byams ma'i bu gang po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-25: tshe dang ldan pa k'a ty'a ya na chen po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-26: tshe dang ldan pa ma 'gags pa dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-27: tshe dang ldan pa re ba ta dang /
T03TD3790.3E:341b-28: tshe dang ldan pa sgra gcan zin dang /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-0: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten bcom ldan 'das kyis @342a * //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-1: gsungs pa la yi rangs te mngon par bstod do /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-3: // / phun sum tshogs gnyis 'byung ba bde ba'i go 'phang 'jig rten rnams kyis thob bya'i phyir //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-4: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje ldan pa'i thugs kyis gang zhig rab tu gsal mdzad pa //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-5: ma lus chos kyi de nyid gnas gyur mdo 'di don du gnyer bas thos gyur nas //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-6: rang gi gnas su song la nyin dang mtshan du mnyam par gzhag pas bsgom par gyis //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-7: lta ba mang pos kun du dkrugs pas de ltar rtsod pa'i dus 'dir klog pa'ang shin tu nyung //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-8: glegs bam du ma'i tshig rnams mi mthun tha dad gyur pa mthong nas dad pas 'dir //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-9: rgol ba'i glang po'i dbang po khros pas 'ong ba'i klad 'gems seng ge bzang po bdag //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-10: gang gis dag par gtugs pa 'jig rten don du mnyam par gzhag pa mkhas pas blang bar gyis //
T03TD3790.3E:342a-11: 'phags pa bcom ldan 'das ma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan gyi rjes su 'brangs nas dag par gtugs pa phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-12: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-14: rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yum /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-19: chos rin po che mi zad pa'i gter /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-21: chos rmad du byung ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mig tu gyur pa /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-24: lha ma yin du bcas pas phyag byas pa bde ba thams cad kyi rgyud rdzogs so /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-26: // / bal yul yam bu'i bsod nams rgyun 'byung gi gtsug lag khang du pandi ta zhi ba bzang po dang /
T03TD3790.3E:342a-27: lo ts'a ba dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
